ent's%20executive%20order%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-orders-federal-dei-roles-terminated-staff-on-leave-immediately-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edismantle%3C%2Fa%3E%20federal%20government%20diversity%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20inclusion%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20executive%20order%20threatens%20public%20services%20that%20benefit%20all%20Americans%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20NAACP%20president%20and%20CEO%2C%20Derrick%20Johnson%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20attempt%20to%20consolidate%20power%20and%20money%20to%20a%20few%20wealthy%20individuals.%20And%20poor%20and%20working-class%20people%20will%20pay%20the%20price.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20critical%20time%20for%20the%20NAACP%2C%20and%20Aba%20Blankson%2C%20its%20chief%20marketing%20and%20communications%20officer.%20There's%20no%20shortage%20of%20issues%2C%20but%20Blankson%20has%20the%20chops%20to%20handle%20them%3A%20She's%20been%20the%20NAACP's%20top%20marketer%20since%202017%2C%20following%20roles%20at%20Common%20Application%20and%20USAID.%20Key%20programs%20during%20her%20tenure%20include%20social%20advocacy%20campaigns%2C%20and%20the%20%23CovidUnmasked%20series%20that%20exposed%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20pandemic%20on%20Black%20communities%20across%20health%2C%20employment%2C%20and%20housing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20CMOs%2C%20she's%20working%20out%20the%20applications%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20conducting%20stakeholder%20research%2C%20and%20advising%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20C-suite%20on%20where%20the%20brand%20needs%20to%20show%20up.%20In%202024%2C%20Washington%20Women%20in%20Public%20Relations%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwwpr.org%2Fwashington-women-in-public-relations-announces-2024-woman-of-the-year-winner%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enamed%20her%20%26quot%3BWoman%20of%20the%20Year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAba%20is%20a%20luminary%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rebecca%20Lowell%20Edwards%2C%20the%20former%20chief%20communications%20and%20marketing%20officer%20at%20the%20ACLU%20who%20is%20now%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.organon.com%2Fmeta-en%2Fleadership%2Frebecca-lowell-edwards%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOrganon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20an%20email.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20at%20the%20ACLU%2C%20I%20would%20often%20watch%20with%20admiration%20what%20she%20was%20doing%20to%20engage%20the%20NAACP%20community%20and%20captivate%20a%20competitive%20landscape%20to%20gain%20attention%20for%20weighty%20topics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEdwards%20said%20Blankson's%20role%20demands%20a%20complex%20amalgam%20of%20skills%20and%20passion.%26quot%3BYou%20are%20operating%20on%20multiple%20speeds%2C%20across%20different%20complex%20subjects%20matters%20with%20deep%20personal%20resonance%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20to%20know%20the%20mechanics%20of%20organizing%2C%20marketing%2C%20brand-building%2C%20and%20every%20other%20essential%20organizational%20discipline%20while%20keeping%20your%20heart%20and%20soul%20intact%20and%20out%20in%20front.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlankson%20said%20NAACP%20has%20had%20to%20keep%20evolving%20the%20way%20it%20inspires%20action%20and%20awareness.%20One%20way%20is%20by%20driving%20investment%20into%20minority-owned%20startups%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnaacp.org%2Farticles%2Fnaacp-launches-innovative-200-million-fund-funds-transform-venture-capital-landscape%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20through%20its%20first%20VC%20fund%20of%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20launched%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20Black%20History%20Month%2C%20the%20NAACP%20gears%20up%20for%20something%20completely%20different%3A%20the%20launch%20of%20a%20new%20daytime%20drama%20titled%20%26quot%3BBeyond%20the%20Gates%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20it%20has%20co-produced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20publicity%20photo%20for%20the%20new%20daytime%20drama%20Beyond%20the%20Gates%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a244ab7bb3f854015bac40%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222143%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BBeyond%20the%20Gates%26quot%3B%20will%20premiere%20on%20February%2024.%3Cp%3EQuantrell%20Colbert%2FCBS%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2235355e72-d954-42cb-bfd9-59f7433d5be4%5C%22%3EBringing%20a%20fresh%20story%20to%20the%20small%20screen%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeyond%20the%20Gates%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20new%20daytime%20drama%20premiering%20on%20February%2024%20on%20CBS%2C%20is%20an%20outcome%20of%20the%20NAACP's%20efforts%20to%20foster%20more%20diverse%20storytelling.%20Produced%20by%20CBS%20Studios%20and%20the%20NAACP%2C%20in%20partnership%20with%20P%26amp%3BG%20Studios%2C%20a%20division%20of%20Procter%20%26amp%3B%20Gamble%2C%20it's%20the%20first%20new%20daytime%20drama%20launched%20by%20a%20major%20TV%20network%20since%201999.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20series%20focuses%20on%20an%20affluent%20Black%20family%2C%20the%20Duprees%2C%20living%20in%20a%20Maryland%20suburb.%20The%20show%20is%20a%20direct%20outcome%20of%20a%20development%20deal%20between%20CBS%20Studios%20and%20NAACP%20that%20began%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20taken%20nearly%20five%20years%20to%20bring%20the%20project%20to%20life.%20That's%20showbiz%2C%20said%20Blankson.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20know%20anything%20about%20the%20television%20landscape%2C%20it%20takes%20a%20long%20time%20for%20projects%20to%20make%20their%20way%20through%20their%20pipeline%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProcter%20%26amp%3B%20Gamble%20was%20the%20pioneer%20of%20the%20so-called%20soap%20opera%20genre%2C%20and%20is%20coproducing.%20Kimberly%20Doebereiner%2C%20the%20head%20of%20P%26amp%3BG%20Studios%20says%20the%20company%20is%20proud%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20new%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20thrilled%20to%20continue%20P%26amp%3BG's%20legacy%20as%20a%20pioneer%20in%20the%20genre%2C%26quot%3B%20Doebereiner%20said%20in%20an%20email%20to%20BI.%20%26quot%3BWe%20value%20finding%20interesting%20ways%20for%20our%20brands%20to%20connect%20with%20people%20around%20relevant%20and%20resonant%20stories.%20We%20hope%20people%20will%20fall%20in%20love%20watching%20the%20Duprees!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22644b0096-3276-457b-8446-652a483fa16e%5C%22%3EA%20campaign%20that%20invokes%202020%20community%20support%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20the%20NAACP%20launched%20an%20advertising%20campaign%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnaacp.org%2Fkeepadvancing%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23KeepAdvancing%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20aims%20to%20reignite%20the%20momentum%20of%202020%20when%20the%20murders%20of%20Breonna%20Taylor%20and%20George%20Floyd%20sparked%20global%20calls%20for%20social%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20time%2C%20allies%20posted%20black%20squares%20on%20their%20social%20media%20accounts%20to%20show%20solidarity%20with%20Black%20justice%20causes.%20The%20gesture%20was%20generally%20perceived%20as%20performative%20and%20was%20subject%20to%20criticism%20and%20ridicule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20individuals%20also%20donated%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20to%20organizations%20like%20NAACP%20at%20the%20time%2C%20Blankson%20confirmed%20that%20only%20one%20in%20three%20of%20those%20donors%20returned%20to%20give%20to%20NAACP%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%23KeepAdvancing%20campaign%2C%20which%20includes%20national%20advertising%2C%20is%20intended%20to%20remind%20allies%20of%20their%20past%20support%20and%20encourage%20them%20to%20take%20direct%20action%20and%20make%20donations%20to%20the%20organization.%20The%20TV%20commercial%20depicts%20a%20woman%20posting%20a%20black%20square%20and%20expressing%20concern%20for%20the%20racial%20justice%20issues%2C%20only%20to%20drift%20away%20as%20life%20events%20overtake%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20some%20ways%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20believe%20that%20it's%20been%20five%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Blankson%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20in%20other%20ways%2C%20it's%20amazing%20that%20we%20haven't%20progressed%20as%20much%20as%20I%20think%20our%20spirit%20wanted%20us%20to%20as%20a%20country.%20Part%20of%20this%20campaign%20is%20really%20to%20challenge%20the%20country%20%E2%80%94%20to%20challenge%20all%20those%20who%20were%20engaged%20in%202020%20to%20say%2C%20'Hey%2C%20the%20work%20is%20not%20done%2C%20we%20need%20you%20now%20more%20than%20ever.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlankson%20said%20the%20campaign%20launch%20ahead%20of%20the%20election%20was%20intentional%2C%20as%20the%20issues%20persist%20regardless%20of%20the%20party%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BElections%20are%20not%20necessarily%20about%20presidential%20candidates%20per%20se%2C%20but%20about%20the%20mood%20of%20the%20country%2C%20where%20the%20country%20is%20going%2C%26quot%3B%20Blankson%20said.%20%26quot%3BNo%20matter%20what%20happened%2C%20we%20knew%20that%20we%20needed%20to%20get%20people%20engaged.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%229504%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20smiling%20while%20outside%20sitting%20at%20a%20table%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6793a54210c98eace913c812%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%226336%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBlankson%20has%20been%20CMO%20at%20NAACP%20since%202017%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20NAACP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e60aeed1-b460-4b52-85f8-be4251ab14d4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20changing%20state%20of%20corporate%20DEI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBlankson%20declined%20to%20give%20specific%20details%20of%20any%20campaign%20the%20NAACP%20will%20undertake%20to%20persuade%20companies%20to%20retain%20DEI.%20She%20said%20she%20has%20met%20with%20many%20companies%20over%20the%20past%20year%20and%20heard%20firsthand%20the%20trepidation%20of%20leaders%20wary%20of%20backlash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20level%20of%20fear%2C%20'We're%20going%20to%20be%20attacked%20if%20we%20don't%20dismantle%20our%20DEI%20programs%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20big%20shift%20from%202020%20when%20companies%20sought%20the%20NAACP's%20advice%20on%20speaking%20publicly%20about%20their%20DEI%20initiatives.%20%26quot%3BI%20personally%20reviewed%20a%20lot%20of%20statements%20in%202020%2C%26quot%3B%20Blankson%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20always%20say%20to%20companies%20that%20if%20it's%20authentic%20to%20your%20company%20and%20your%20company's%20culture%2C%20then%20it%20is%20right.%20If%20it's%20not%2C%20then%20it's%20not.%20If%20you%20can%20maintain%20it%20in%20the%20difficult%20times%2C%20then%20it's%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlankson%20said%20the%20purchasing%20power%20of%20Black%20consumers%20will%20exert%20influence%20on%20these%20decisions.%20Though%20estimates%20vary%2C%20McKinsey%20%26amp%3B%20Company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mckinsey.com%2Ffeatured-insights%2Fthemes%2Fthe-state-of-black-consumers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epredicts%3C%2Fa%3E%20Black%20purchasing%20power%20will%20grow%20to%20%241.7%20trillion%20by%202030.%20%26quot%3BCompanies%20cutting%20DEI%20practices%20%E2%80%94%20effectively%20turning%20their%20backs%20on%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20their%20customer%20base%20%E2%80%94%20will%20eventually%20come%20to%20recognize%20this%20reality%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Blankson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENixing%20DEI%20initiatives%20can%20complicate%20things%20for%20brand%20marketing.%20Case%20in%20point%2C%20Walmart%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-latest-company-walk-back-dei-initiatives-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erolled%20back%20some%20of%20its%20DEI%20initiatives%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20November%3B%20the%20following%20month%2C%20the%20company%20faced%20backlash%20on%20social%20media%20for