3EThen%20there's%20the%20hot-button%20topic%20on%20many%20marketers'%20minds%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feinat-weiss-nice-cmo-ai-marketing-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Blankson%2C%20like%20many%20CMOs%2C%20is%20figuring%20out%20what%20AI%20use%20cases%20will%20help%20the%20organization%20and%20what%20rules%20are%20needed%20to%20protect%20its%20IP%20and%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20were%20developing%20our%20own%20set%20of%20commercials%2C%20there%20came%20a%20point%20where%20we%20said%2C%20'This%20part%20of%20the%20video%20isn't%20quite%20right.%20Can%20we%20use%20AI%20to%20fix%20this%3F'%20But%20then%20if%20you%20do%20that%2C%20what%20is%20the%20disclosure%3F%26quot%3B%20Blankson%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20whole%20new%20landscape%2C%20and%20I%20know%20that%20my%20CMO%20colleagues%20are%20grappling%20with%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20NAACP%20approaches%20its%20116th%20anniversary%20this%20month%2C%20Blankson%20said%20the%20organization's%20secret%20to%20enduring%20relevance%20is%20adapting%20to%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20example%20is%20the%20launch%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnaacp.org%2Farticles%2Fnaacp-launches-innovative-200-million-fund-funds-transform-venture-capital-landscape%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENAACP%20Capital%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20fund%20that's%20raising%20%24200%20million%20to%20invest%20in%20fund%20managers%20committed%20to%20closing%20investment%20gaps%20for%20people%20of%20color.%20%26quot%3BWe%20know%20that%20African-Americans%20in%20particular%20get%20less%20of%20the%20capital%20funds%20that%20are%20available%2C%20and%20our%20entrepreneurs%20have%20great%20ideas%20that%20they%20want%20to%20bring%20to%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20Blankson%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we%20have%20started%20a%20VC%20fund%20to%20try%20to%20close%20that%20gap.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NAACP's%20historical%20legacy%20looms