%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.annefrankexhibit.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BAnne%20Frank%20The%20Exhibition%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20immersive%20experience%20at%20the%20%3Cspan%3ECenter%20for%20Jewish%20History%20near%20%3C%2Fspan%3EUnion%20Square%2C%20features%20a%20full-scale%20replica%20of%20the%20Secret%20Annex%20where%20Anne%20and%20her%20family%20lived%20in%20hiding%20in%20Amsterdam%20for%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20annex%20is%20furnished%20just%20as%20it%20was%20during%20the%20Franks'%20years%20in%20seclusion%2C%20allowing%20visitors%20to%20experience%20the%20space%20as%20they%20did%20and%20gain%20a%20deeper%20understanding%20of%20the%20day-to-day%20lives%20of%20Anne%2C%20her%20family%2C%20and%20the%20others%20who%20lived%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20exhibition%20arrives%20at%20a%20time%20when%20teaching%20the%20lessons%20of%20history%20is%20urgent%2C%26quot%3B%20Ronald%20Leopold%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Anne%20Frank%20House%2C%20which%20has%20partnered%20with%20the%20Center%20for%20Jewish%20History%20to%20create%20the%20exhibit%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAcross%20the%20United%20States%20and%20around%20the%20world%2C%20we%20are%20witnessing%20a%20troubling%20rise%20in%20antisemitism%20and%20other%20forms%20of%20group%20hatred.%20The%20Anne%20Frank%20House%20has%20always%20felt%20a%20deep%20responsibility%20to%20counter%20these%20forces%20through%20education%2C%20and%20this%20exhibition%20is%20a%20powerful%20response%20to%20that%20mission.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhotos%20show%20inside%20the%20new%20exhibition%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnne%20Frank%20The%20Exhibit%20is%20located%20in%20Union%20Square%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221734%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22anne%20frank%20house%20exhibition%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a11679bfebcc