terdam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20actual%20Anne%20Frank%20House%20is%20unfurnished%2C%20making%20this%20exhibit%20the%20only%20way%20to%20see%20how%20the%20annex%2C%20which%20occupied%20two%20full%20floors%2C%20an%20attic%20space%2C%20and%20a%20loft%20inside%20the%20home%2C%20would%20have%20looked%20between%201942%20and%201944.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20rooms%20are%20fully%20recreated%20and%20furnished%20to%20scale%20according%20to%20how%20they%20looked%20when%20the%20Franks%20lived%20there.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22anne%20frank%20house%20exhibition%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a116797bb3f854015b8b3a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221734%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERonald%20Leopold%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Anne%20Frank%20House%2C%20inside%20the%20exhibit.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Halpern%2FAnne%20Frank%20The%20Exhibition%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnne%20was%2013%20when%20she%20moved%20to%20the%20Annex%20with%20her%20mother%2C%20Edith%3B%20her%20father%2C%20Otto%3B%20and%20her%20older%20sister%2C%20Margot%2C%2016.%20Four%20others%20also%20lived%20with%20them%3A%20Hermann%20and%20Auguste%20van%20Pels%2C%20their%2015-year-old%20son%20Peter%2C%20and%20Fritz%20Pfeffer%2C%20a%20dentist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20York%20City%20exhibition%20spans%20over%207%2C500%20square%20feet%20of%20gallery%20space%20between%20the%20recreated%20rooms%20and%20a%20separate%20space%20with%20photographs%20and%20other%20artifacts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20recreated%20Annex%20is%20not%20just%20a%20historical%20space%3B%20it%20is%20a%20gateway%20to%20understanding%20the%20past%20and%2C%20crucially%2C%20learning%20from%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Leopold%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20move%20further%20into%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20it%20is%20imperative%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20engage%20new%20generations%20with%20Anne's%20story.%20While%20rooted%20in%20a%20specific%20historical%20moment%2C%20her%20experiences%20resonate%20far%20beyond%20her%20time%2C%20speaking%20to%20our%20shared%20humanity%20and%20the%20moral%20choices%20we%20all%20face%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BThis%20exhibition%20does%20more%20than%20remember%20Anne%3B%20it%20challenges%20each%20visitor%20to%20reflect%20on%20how%20history%20can%20inform%20our%20responses%20to%20hatred%20and%20injustice%20in%20our%20own%20communities%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Franks%20went%20into%20hiding%20in%20the%20summer%20of%201942%20and%20were%20joined%20a%20week%20later%20by%20the%20Van%20Pels%20family.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22anne%20frank%20house%20exhibition%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a1167fbfebcc4d029d9258%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221734%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20kitchen%20of%20the%20Secret%20Annex.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Halpern%2FAnne%20Frank%20The%20Exhibition%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Franks%2C%20who%20had%20left%20Germany%20for%20Amsterdam%20in%20the%201930s%2C%20moved%20into%20the%20Secret%20Annex%2C%20as%20it%20came%20to%20be%20known%2C%20after%20Margot%20received%20a%20summons%20to%20report%20to%20a%20labor%20camp%20in%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20entrance%20was%20located%20behind%20a%20bookcase%20in%20the%20back%20of%20Otto%20Frank's%20office%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ground%20floor%20of%20the%20office%20building%20was%20used%20as%20a%20workshop%20for%20the%20Pectacon%20company%2C%20which%20sold%20herbs%20and%20spices%2C%20and%20the%20first%20and%20second%20floors%20were%20used%20as%20storage%20and%20office%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20staircase%20was%20later%20constructed%20to%20lead%20from%20the%20main%20house's%20first%20floor%20to%20the%20second%20floor.%20It%20opened%20out%20onto%20a%20landing%20where%2C%20when%20the%20Franks%20entered%20into%20hiding%2C%20a%20revolving%20bookcase%20was%20placed%20in%20front%20of%20a%20door%20that%20entered%20into%20the%20annex.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20annex's%20inhabitants%20lived%20there%20for%20two%20years%20in%20complete%20secrecy%2C%20aside%20from%20a%20small%20number%20of%20helpers%20who%20provided%20them%20with%20food%20and%20other%20supplies.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22anne%20frank%20house%20exhibition%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a1169f7bb3f854015b8b44%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221734%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20kitchen%20of%20the%20Secret%20Annex.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Halpern%2FAnne%20Frank%20The%20Exhibition%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20families%20lived%20primarily%20on%20the%20second%20and%20third%20floors%20of%20the%20building%2C%20above%20the%20warehouse%20on%20the%20ground%20floor%20and%20office%20building%20on%20the%20first%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20members%20of%20the%20office%20staff%2C%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bhelpers%2C%26quot%3B%20knew%20about%20the%20people%20hiding%20in%20the%20annex%20and%20helped%20to%20conceal%20them%20from%20the%20warehouse%20workers%20and%20outsiders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20annex%20had%20a%20kitchen%2C%20a%20bathroom%2C%20and%20rooms%20that%20could%20be%20converted%20into%20bedrooms%20at%20night.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22anne%20frank%20house%20exhibition%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a1168dbfebcc4d029d925f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221734%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOtto%2C%20Edith%2C%20and%20Margot%20Frank's%20room%20inside%20the%20Secret%20Annex.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Halpern%2FAnne%20Frank%20The%20Exhibition%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bathroom%20had%20a%20sink%20and%20toilet%2C%20which%20the%20eight%20inhabitants%20shared%2C%20requiring%20them%20to%20take%20turns%20using%20them%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20at%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20night%2C%20the%20kitchen%20and%20dining%20room%20was%20converted%20into%20Hermann%20and%20Auguste%20van%20Pels'%20bedroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDuring%20the%20day%2C%20the%20bedroom%20of%20Otto%2C%20Edith%2C%20and%20Margot%20Frank%20acted%20as%20the%20Frank%20family's%20living%20room.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22anne%20frank%20house%20exhibition%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a116867bb3f854015b8b3f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221734%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOtto%2C%20Edith%2C%20and%20Margot%20Frank's%20room%20inside%20the%20Secret%20Annex.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Halpern%2FAnne%20Frank%20The%20Exhibition%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESpace%20was%20limited%20inside%20the%20annex%2C%20so%20it%20was%20vital%20for%20the%20inhabitants%20to%20rely%20on%20each%20other%20for%20support%20and%20to%20share%20the%20space%20peacefully.%20In%20the%20morning%2C%20the%20families%20had%20to%20wear%20socks%20and%20be%20as%20quiet%20as%20possible%20so%20as%20not%20to%20tip%20off%20the%20warehouse%20or%20office%20workers%20about%20their%20movements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20enjoyed%20a%20quick%20reprieve%20during%20the%20weekday%20lunch%20break%2C%20when%20the%20helpers%20would%20come%20up%20to%20the%20annex%20for%20lunch%20and%20discuss%20the%20latest%20news%20from%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20the%20afternoon%2C%20the%20family%20would%20nap%20or%20do%20quiet%20activities%20like%20reading%20or%20writing.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22anne%20frank%20house%20exhibition%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a1168dbfebcc4d029d925e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221734%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20letter-writing%20desk%20was%20placed%20inside%20Otto%2C%20Edith%2C%20and%20Margot%20Frank's%20room.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Halpern%2FAnne%20Frank%20The%20Exhibition%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20workday%20ended%20around%206%20p.m.%2C%20the%20annex%20inhabitants%20were%20able%20to%20move%20freely%20about%20the%20entire%20office%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20standard%20evening%20inside%20the%20annex%20involved%20Otto%20Frank%20writing%20business%20letters%20on%20the%20typewriter%20and%20Margot%20and%20Anne%20doing%20various%20chores%20around%20the%20house.%20The%20two%20older%20women%20would%20also%20cook%20dinner%20for%20everyone%20in%20hiding%20using%20the%20supplies%20brought%20to%20them%20by%20the%20helpers%2C%20according%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.annefrank.org%2Fen%2Fanne-frank%2Fgo-in-depth%2Ftypical-day-secret-annex%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnne%20Frank%20House%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20the%20war%20raged%20on%20and%20access%20to%20high-quality%20food%20dwindled%2C%20food%20became%20less%20and%20less%20appetizing%20to%20the%20family%2C%20and%20especially%20to%20Anne.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBlech%2C%20the%20mere%20thought%20that%20I%20have%20to%20eat%20that%20swill%20makes%20me%20nauseated%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20in%20her%20diary%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Anne%20Frank%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20dinner%2C%20the%20families%20would%20relax%20by%20reading%2C%20conversing%2C%20or%20listening%20to%20the%20radio%20before%20transforming%20their%20living%20areas%20into%20bedrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20sun%20set%2C%20the%20windows%20would%20also%20be%20blacked%20out%20in%20order%20to%20conceal%20the%20family%20moving%20about%20the%20annex%2C%20and%20they%20would%20all%20have%20to%20be%20silent%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnne%20Frank%20shared%20a%20room%20with%20Fritz%20Pfeffer%2C%20who%20was%20the%20same%20age%20as%20her%20father.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22anne%20frank%20house%20exhibition%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a11679bfebcc4d029d9256%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221734%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnne%20Frank%20and%20Fritz%20Pfeffer's%20room%20inside%20the%20annex.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Halpern%2FAnne%20Frank%20The%20Exhibition%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pair%20fought%20over%20the%20use%20of%20the%20writing%20desk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnne%2C%20a%20spirited%20teenager%2C%20felt%20that%20desk%20time%20should%20be%20split%20evenly%20between%20herself%20and%20Pfeffer%2C%20but%20he%20disagreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOtto%20eventually%20intervened%20in%20the%20conflict%20over%20the%20writing%20desk%2C%20which%20Frank%20wrote%20about%20in%20her%20diary.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22anne%20frank%20house%20exhibition%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a11679eb4be2fff9a34d5d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221734%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPhotographs%20above%20Anne%20Frank's%20desk.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Halpern%2FAnne%20Frank%20The%20Exhibition%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPfeffer%20looked%20very%20sullen%2C%20didn't%20talk%20to%20me%20for%20two%20days%20and%20made%20a%20point%20of%20sitting%20at%20the%20table%20from%205%20to%205.30%20anyway...%20childish%2C%20of%20course%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Anne%20Frank%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPeter%2C%20the%20van%20Pels'%20teenage%20son%2C%20was%20the%20only%20inhabitant%20to%20have%20their%20own%20room%20in%20the%20annex.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22anne%20frank%20house%20exhibition%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a116927bb3f854015b8b42%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221734%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeter%20van%20Pels'%20room%20inside%20the%20secret%20annex.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Halpern%2FAnne%20Frank%20The%20Exhibition%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20is%20speculated%20about%20Peter%20and%20Anne's%20relationship.%20She%20wrote%20that%20she%20wasn't%20very%20fond%20of%20him%20when%20he%20and%20his%20family%20first%20moved%20into%20the%20annex.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20romantic%20spark%20soon%20developed%20between%20the%20pair%2C%20who%20were%20both%20longing%20for%20someone%20to%20talk%20to%20about%20their%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20her%20first%20kiss%20with%20him%20on%20the%20bed%20of%20his%20small%20room%20below%20the%20annex's%20attic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20fully%20recreated%20annex%2C%20there%20are%20photos%20of%20the%20family%20and%20the%20war%20at%20the%20exhibition.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22anne%20frank%20house%20exhibition%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a11682bfebcc4d029d925a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221734%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPhotos%20along%20the%20walls%20inside%20Anne%20Frank%20The%20Exhibition.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Halpern%2FAnne%20Frank%20The%20Exhibition%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20exhibition%20includes%20more%20than%20100%20original%20collection%20items%2C%20from%20Anne%20Frank's%20first%20photo%20album%20to%20handwritten%20verses%20written%20by%20Anne%20Frank%20in%20her%20friends'%20poetry%20albums.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20exhibit%20is%20the%20first%20opportunity%20for%20the%20public%20to%20see%20what%20the%20annex%20would%20have%20looked%20like%20completely%20furnished.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22anne%20frank%20house%20exhibition%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a11686bfebcc4d029d925c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221734%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPhotos%20along%20the%20walls%20inside%20Anne%20Frank%20The%20Exhibition.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Halpern%2FAnne%20Frank%20The%20Exhibition%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOtto%20Frank%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22h