.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Felon-musk-is-the-idol-of-doges-youngest-staff-edward-coristine-who-founded-tesla-sexy-llc%2Farticleshow%2F117985729.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F117985729.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk's%20Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%2C%20staffed%20by%20young%20individuals%20like%2019-year-old%20Edward%20Coristine%2C%20has%20raised%20concerns%20over%20access%20to%20sensitive%20government%20data.%20Coristine%2C%20a%20freshman%20dropout%20and%20entrepreneur%2C%20had%20established%20numerous%20companies%20and%20briefly%20worked%20at%20Neuralink%20before%20joining%20DOGE.%20He%20was%20present%20at%20the%20crucial%20meeting%20where%20government%20staff%20were%20asked%20to%20justify%20their%20jobs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Felon-musk-is-the-idol-of-doges-youngest-staff-edward-coristine-who-founded-tesla-sexy-llc%2Farticleshow%2F117985729.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Felon-musk-is-the-idol-of-doges-youngest-staff-edward-coristine-who-founded-tesla-sexy-llc%2Famp_articleshow%2F117985729.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Felon-musk-is-the-idol-of-doges-youngest-staff-edward-coristine-who-founded-tesla-sexy-llc%2Famp_articleshow%2F117985729.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Is%20South%20Cinema%20Finally%20Done%20With%20Violence%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETelugu%20film%3Cem%3E%20Sankranthiki%20Vasthunam%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20made%20for%20family%20audiences%2C%20was%20released%20on%20January%2014%20this%20year%20and%20has%20reportedly%20grossed%20an%20impressive%20Rs%20300%20crore%20worldwide%20in%20three%20weeks.%20Directed%20by%20Anil%20Ravipudi%2C%20the%20film%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20highest-grossing%20Telugu%20film%20for%20Sankranti%20this%20year%2C%20surpassing%20director%20Shankar's%20Ram%20Charan-starrer%2C%20%3Cem%3EGame%20Changer%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Notably%2C%20both%20films%20were%20produced%20by%20Dil%20Raju.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Tamil%20cinema%2C%20director%20Sundar%20C's%20%3Cem%3EMadha%20Gaja%20Raja%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20struck%20a%20chord%20with%20family%20audiences%2C%20reportedly%20netting%20more%20than%20Rs%2055%20crore%20at%20the%20box%20office%20since%20its%20release%20on%20January%2012.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20Tamil-language%20%3Cem%3EKudumbasthan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20modest%20family%20film%2C%20is%20said%20to%20have%20collected%20around%20Rs%2018%20crore%20since%20its%20release%20on%20January%2024.%20The%20success%20of%20these%20films%20raises%20an%20intriguing%20question%3A%20are%20family%20movies%20making%20a%20comeback%20in%20South%20cinema%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELearning%20From%20A%20Poor%202024%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20year%202024%20was%20challenging%20for%20the%20South%20Indian%20film%20industry%2C%20with%20significant%20losses%20reported%20across%20the%20board.%20The%20Malayalam%20film%20industry%20reportedly%20faced%20losses%20of%20Rs%20700%20crore%2C%20while%20the%20Tamil%20film%20industry%20saw%20a%20deficit%20of%20around%20Rs%201%2C000%20crore.%20Several%20big-budget%20films%2C%20including%20%3Cem%3EIndian%202%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EKanguva%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3EGame%20Changer%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20failed%20to%20ignite%20the%20box%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20this%20backdrop%2C%20the%20success%20of%20films%20like%20%3Cem%3ESankranthiki%20Vasthunam%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EMadha%20Gaja%20Raja%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%20surprised%20many.%20Interestingly%2C%20Anil%20Ravipudi's%20film%20does%20not%20feature%20an%20A-list%20cast%2C%20instead%20starring%2064-year-old%20Venkatesh%20alongside%20Meenakshi%20Dixit%20and%20Aishwarya%20Rajesh.%20And%2C%20%3Cem%3EMadha%20Gaja%20Raja%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20featuring%20Vishal%2C%20Santhanam%2C%20Anjali%2C%20and%20Varalaxmi%20Sarathkumar%2C%20was%20completed%20in%202013%20but%20couldn't%20be%20released%20for%2012%20years%20due%20to%20legal%20and%20financial%20issues.%20It%20finally%20hit%20theatres%20in%20January%202025.%20%3Cem%3EKudumbasthan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20starring%20actor-writer%20Manikandan%2C%20who%20is%20known%20for%20relatable%2C%20crowd-pleasing%20films%2C%20has%20also%20drawn%20significant%20family%20audiences.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPause%20The%20Action%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20Indian%20cinema%20largely%20followed%20the%20trend%20of%20previous%20years%2C%20with%20a%20flood%20of%20action-packed%20films%20aimed%20at%20younger%20audiences.%20Kollywood%20witnessed%20releases%20like%20%3Cem%3ERaayan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EGarudan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3ECaptain%20Miller%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EKanguva%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3EThangalaan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20while%20Tollywood%20saw%20films%20such%20as%20%3Cem%3EDevara%3A%20Part%201%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3ESaripodhaa%20Sanivaaram%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EEagle%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3EGuntur%20Kaaram%3C%2Fem%3E.%20However%2C%20the%20tide%20seemed%20to%20turn%20when%20Sivakarthikeyan's%20%3Cem%3EAmaran%20was%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ereleased%20on%20October%2031.%20It%20resonated%20with%20family%20audiences%2C%20grossing%20nearly%20Rs%20340%20crore%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20this%20shift%2C%20film%20journalist%20Bharath%20Kumar%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20film%20industry%20had%20been%20focused%20on%20action%20dramas%20and%20thrillers%2C%20neglecting%20family-oriented%20stories.%20Family%20audiences%20were%20not%20prioritised%2C%20as%20most%20films%20catered%20to%20younger%20viewers%20seeking%20action-packed%20narratives.%20In%202024%2C%20many%20big%20action%20films%20failed%20to%20capture%20even%20the%20youth%20market.%20Family%20entertainers%2C%20which%20blend%20sentiment%2C%20drama%2C%20comedy%2C%20and%20a%20feel-good%20factor%2C%20have%20now%20found%20favour%20with%20audiences.%20The%20success%20of%20these%20films%20in%20January%202025%20demonstrates%20a%20growing%20demand%20for%20fresh%2C%20wholesome%20content%20without%20violence%20and%20noise.%20People%20want%20to%20come%20to%20theatres%2C%20enjoy%20a%20good%20laugh%2C%20and%20leave%20happy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFamily%20Viewing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20films%20offer%20a%20refreshing%20alternative%20to%20darker%2C%20more%20intense%20genres%20like%20action%20and%20thrillers.%20These%20films%20also%20allow%20groups%20and%20families%20to%20visit%20theatres%20together%2C%20a%20trend%20that%20had%20been%20waning.%20In%20a%20recent%20interview%2C%20actor%20Manikandan%20explained%20that%20%3Cem%3EKudumbasthan%20%3C%2Fem%3Eexplores%20the%20struggles%20of%20a%20family%20man%20in%20today's%20digital%20world%20through%20a%20humorous%20lens.%20He%20described%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20adventurous%20ride%20of%20a%20family%20man%20and%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20a%20married%20woman%26quot%3B.%20The%20film's%20relatable%20content%20has%20earned%20praise%20from%20critics%20and%20audiences%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%202025%20off%20to%20a%20promising%20start%20for%20family%20entertainers%2C%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20this%20trend%20will%20last%20through%20the%20year.%20Producers%20may%20now%20be%20encouraged%20to%20invest%20in%20such%20films%2C%20especially%20given%20the%20waning%20popularity%20of%20big%20action%20flicks.%20The%20tide%20might%20just%20be%20turning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20a%20senior%20entertainment%20journalist%20and%20film%20critic)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738848240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fimagesvs.oneindia.com%2Fimg%2F2025%2F01%2Fsankranthiki-vasthunam-review-01-1736827597.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fis-south-cinema-finally-done-with-violence-7649636%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20success%20of%20Anil%20Ravipudi's%20'Sankranthiki%20Vasthunam'%2C%20Sundar%20Cs%20'Madha%20Gaja%20Raja'%2C%20and%20Rajeshwar%20Kalaisamy's%20'Kudumbasthan'%20indicates%20that%20producers%20may%20finally%20be%20turning%20to%20family%20entertainers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fis-south-cinema-finally-done-with-violence-7649636%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Ghar%20mein%20sun-ne%20nahi%20milega'%3A%20PM%20Modi's%20praise%2C%20dig%20and%20shayari%20for%20Kharge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738847932000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117985572%2Cimgsize-1111477.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Faapko-toh-ghar-mein-sunne-nahi-milega-pm-modis-praise-dig-and-shayari-dedication-for-kharge%2Farticleshow%2F117985588.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20dedicated%20a%20shayari%20to%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20lauding%20his%20public%20service%20while%20also%20aiming%20a%20dig%20at%20him.%20Modi%20criticized%20the%20Gandhi%20family%2C%20recalled%20the%20Nehru%20era%20and%20the%20Emergency%2C%20and%20recited%20lines%20from%20poet%20Neeraj%20to%20highlight%20Congress's%20challenges%20during%20his%20reply%20to%20the%20President's%20address.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Faapko-toh-ghar-mein-sunne-nahi-milega-pm-modis-praise-dig-and-shayari-dedication-for-kharge%2Farticleshow%2F117985588.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3