ings.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20hasn't%20always%20been%20easy%2C%20but%20it%20has%20paid%20off%20by%20making%20me%20more%20thoughtful%20about%20how%20I%20spend%20money.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20was%20forced%20to%20move%20out%20of%20my%20one-bedroom%2C%20rent-controlled%20bungalow%20in%20West%20Los%20Angeles%20when%20developers%20bought%20it%20and%20planned%20to%20tear%20it%20down%20and%20replace%20it%20with%20a%20mixed-use%20building.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20only%20four%20months%20to%20find%20a%20place%2C%20I%20panicked.%20After%20doing%20some%20apartment%20hunting%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20asking%20my%20local%20friends%20if%20they%20knew%20of%20any%20rentals%20that%20fit%20my%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fbest-budgeting-apps%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebudget%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20I%20soon%20realized%20that%20I%20would%20have%20to%20double%20my%20costs%2C%20move%20outside%20the%20city%2C%20or%20get%20a%20roommate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2292a804a4-98a8-4b89-9566-af1df029a651%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20moved%20to%20a%20tiny%20house%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20searching%20primarily%20in%20West%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20Mid-City%2C%20and%20Highland%20Park%2C%20I%20settled%20more%20east%20near%20Pasadena.%20I%20stumbled%20across%20a%20tiny%20cabin%20in%20a%20compound%20on%20a%20Facebook%20listing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20home%20was%20in%20a%20canyon%20area%20nestled%20by%20a%20flowing%20creek.%20The%20photos%20didn't%20depict%20the%20place%20accurately%2C%20and%20it%20was%20much%20more%20pleasant%20when%20I%20viewed%20it%20in%20person.%20That%20meant%20fewer%20people%20likely%20applied%2C%20which%20boosted%20my%20odds%20of%20landing%20the%20apartment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20I%20would%20be%20fo