20to%20get%20on%20a%20bed%2C%20it's%20a%20small%20price%20to%20pay%20for%20a%20mattress%20with%20a%20medium-firm%20feel%20that%20keeps%20my%20hips%20lifted%20and%20my%20spine%20aligned%2C%20while%20also%20remaining%20cozy%20and%20comfortable.%20It%20relieves%20any%20pain%20I'm%20experiencing%20with%20a%20night%20or%20two%20of%20sleep.%20Plus%2C%20I%20sleep%20better%20knowing%20that%20I'm%20not%20breathing%20any%20toxic%20or%20allergy-inducing%20materials%20from%20this%20organic%20mattress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22plushbeds%20mattress%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6798047e196626c4098536a2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20PlushBeds%20Botanical%20Bliss%20Organic%20Latex%20Mattress%20is%20my%20go%20to%20mattress%20even%20when%20I'm%20not%20testing%20mattresses.%20It's%20keeps%20my%20hips%20lifted%20and%20my%20spine%20aligned%20while%20sleeping%20cool%20and%20limiting%20motion%20transfer.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mattress%20has%20a%20fully%20organic%20latex%20construction%2C%20including%20materials%20you%20can%20feel%20good%20about%20like%20GOLS-certified%20latex%2C%20GOTS-certified%20organic%20cotton%2C%20and%20GOTS-certified%20organic%20wool.%20The%20mattress'%20support%20comes%20from%20a%20natural%20latex%20layer%20that%20offers%20support%20and%20comfort%2C%20followed%20by%20an%20organic%20latex%20comfort%20layer%2C%20and%20then%20a%20support%20core%20made%20from%20a%20more%20durable%20and%20dense%20dunlop%20latex.%20If%20need%20be%2C%20you%20can%20rearrange%20the%20layers%20of%20the%20mattress%20to%20achieve%20the%20best%20feel%2C%20though%20it's%20unlikely%20you'll%20need%20to%20do%20this%20considering%20you%20can%20choose%20between%20two%20firmness%20options%20and%20three%20thickness%20options%20(%209%2C%2010%2C%20and%2012%20inches).%20I'd%20even%20suggest%20this%20mattress%20to%20those%20who%20are%20combo%20sleepers%20or%20who%20have%20a%20partner%20with%20a%20different%20sleep%20style%20as%20you%20can%20order%20the%20mattress%20in%20split%20sizes%20so%20one%20side%20is%20medium%20and%20the%20other%20side%20is%20medium-firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20its%20eco-credentials%2C%20the%20PlushBeds%20Botanical%20Bliss%20Organic%20Latex%20Mattress%20does%20a%20phenomenal%20job%20at%20motion%20isolation%20and%20breathability.%20It's%20not%20a%20cooling%20mattress%2C%20but%20it%20will%20keep%20you%20temperature%20neutral%20throughout%20the%20night.%20I%20sleep%20with%20a%20heavy%20comforter%20on%20this%20bed%20no%20matter%20the%20season%20(and%20I%20live%20in%20Texas%20where%20the%20summers%20get%20hot!)%20and%20I've%20yet%20to%20feel%20overheated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20admit%20that%20the%20edge%20support%20is%20severely%20lacking.%20When%20I%20lie%20with%20my%20shoulders%20aligned%20to%20the%20edge%2C%20I%20can%20get%20about%2040%20degrees%20before%20I%20feel%20like%20I'm%20about%20to%20fall.%20Plus%2C%20I%20can%20feel%20the%20mattress%20dip%20when%20I%20lie%20too%20close%20to%20the%20edge%2C%20and%20it%20sinks%20four%20inches%20when%20I%20sit%20on%20the%20side%20(for%20reference%2C%20I'm%20180%20pounds.%2C%20so%20it%20could%20sink%20further%20or%20not%20as%20much%20for%20someone%20who%20weighs%20more%20or%20less%20than%20I%20do).%20Fortunately%2C%20it%20excels%20in%20all%20other%20areas%20we%20analyze%20our%20mattresses%20for.%20The%20100-night%20sleep%20trial%20and%20lifetime%20warranty%20are%20also%20helpful%20in%20making%20sure%20this%20mattress%20is%20the%20right%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-organic-mattress%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20organic%20mattress%3C%2Fa%3E%20guide%20for%20more%20sustainably%20made%20mattresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222e9a99ca-2463-4745-846b-7aac3df58a06%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20budget%5C%22%3EBest%20budget%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20let%20the%20budget%20price%20of%20the%2012-inch%20Zinus%20Cooling%20Comfort%20Support%20Hybrid%20Mattress%20fool%20you%2C%20this%20hybrid%20mattress%20is%20a%20great%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-cheap-mattresses%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echeap%20mattress%3C%2Fa%3E%20option%20for%20stomach%20sleepers%20who%20like%20the%20support%20of%20a%20hybrid%20and%20the%20contouring%20cushioning%20of%20memory%20foam%2C%20though%20without%20that%20sink%20in%20feeling.%20Where%20the%20coils%20will%20keep%20your%20hips%20lifted%20and%20your%20spine%20aligned%2C%20the%20gel-infused%20memory%20foam%20will%20offer%20comfort%20as%20you%20sleep%20on%20your%20stomach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20individually%20wrapped%20support%20coils%20respond%20to%20your%20movements%20and%20do%20not%20reverberate%20to%20your%20partner's%20side%20of%20the%20bed.%20This%20results%20in%20better%20sleep%20for%20couples%20as%20you%20won't%20feel%20your%20partner%20move%20at%20night.%20Not%20to%20mention%2C%20the%20coils%20along%20the%20edges%20feel%20secure%2C%20ensuring%20that%20the%20mattress%20edges%20won't%20sag%20and%20you%20can%20comfortably%20get%20in%20and%20out%20of%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20tester%20thought%20the%20mattress%20provided%20good%20pressure%20relief%20no%20matter%20the%20sleep%20position%2C%20and%20has%20yet%20to%20awake%20sore%20come%20morning.%20In%20terms%20of%20keeping%20you%20cool%2C%20the%20hybrid%20design%20automatically%20allows%20for%20more%20airflow.%20The%20gel-infused%20memory%20foam%20works%20against%20your%20body%20heat%2C%20keeping%20you%20cool%20throughout%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20marketed%20as%20a%20medium-plush%2C%20it%20sleeps%20more%20firm%2C%20making%20it%20well-suited%20as%20a%20comfortable%20option%20for%20stomach%20sleepers.%20It%20might%20not%20however%20offer%20enough%20support%20for%20heavy%20sleepers%20over%20250%20pounds%2C%20who%20may%20find%20they%20sink%20in%20too%20far.%20However%2C%20some%20long%20term%20users%20within%20Amazon%20have%20questioned%20its%20long-term%20durability%20or%20sagging.%20It%20is%20backed%20by%20a%2010-year%20warranty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e6b4dc38-18d8-4eb8-ae57-5d2c840900ab%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20hybrid%5C%22%3EBest%20hybrid%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Helix%20Dusk%20Luxe%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20comfortable%20mattresses%20I've%20ever%20slept%20on.%20It%20provides%20a%20bouncy%20and%20cushioned%20feel%20with%20hybrid%20support%20that%20prevents%20your%20body%20from%20sinking%20deeply%20into%20the%20bed.%20I'd%20rate%20it%20highly%20among%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-hybrid-mattress%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20best%20hybrid%20mattressess%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20give%20it%20a%206%20out%20of%2010%20on%20the%20firmness%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Helix%20Dusk%20Luxe%20mattress%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66df0e03a0ff598b2665bf07%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20medium-firm%20Helix%20Dusk%20Luxe%20has%20a%20cushy%20balanced%20feel%20that%20prevents%20your%20body%20from%20sinking%20deeply%20into%20the%20bed%2C%20and%20offers%20upgrades%20for%20cooling%20and%20advanced%20lumbar%20support.%3Cp%3EJaclyn%20Turner%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20responsive%20foam%20layers%20provide%20pressure%20relief%20while%20contouring%20slightly%20around%20your%20body%3B%20the%20individually%20wrapped%20coils%20keep%20your%20spine%20aligned%20when%20lying%20on%20your%20stomach.%20Enhanced%20lumbar%20support%20also%20contributes%20to%20alleviating%20back%20pain.%20We%20also%20love%20it%20for%20back%20sleepers%20too%2C%20looking%20for%20medium-firm%20support.%20The%20edges%20of%20the%20mattress%20are%20reinforced%2C%20but%20sinks%20about%203.5%20inches%2C%20placing%20its%20performance%20as%20squarely%20average%20among%20other%20mattresses.%20In%20terms%20of%20motion%20isolation%2C%20it's%20unlikely%20you'll%20feel%20your%20partner%20getting%20in%20and%20out%20of%20bed%2C%20but%20you%20may%20feel%20them%20change%20positions.%20This%20is%20pretty%20typical%20for%20most%20hybrid%20mattresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Helix%20Dusk%20Luxe%20with%20a%20Tencel%20cover%20did%20an%20average%20job%20at%20regulating%20my%20temperature%20at%20night%20(to%20be%20fair%2C%20I%20tested%20it%20at%20the%20height%20of%20a%20Texas%20summer).%20There%20were%20some%20nights%20where%20I%20grew%20warm%20and%20other%20nights%20I%20didn't.%20For%20reference%2C%20I'm%20not%20a%20hot%20sleeper.%20If%20you%20generally%20run%20warm%20or%20hot%2C%20then%20upgrading%20to%20the%20GlacioTex%20Cooling%20Cover%20is%20well%20worth%20the%20additional%20cost%2C%20as%20my%20editor%20Jaclyn%20Turner%20did%20when%20she%20reviewed%20the%20Helix%20Dusk%20Luxe%2C%20and%20found%20it%20dissipated%20heat%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fhelix-luxe-dusk-mattress-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHelix%20Dusk%20Luxe%20mattress%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222e4f7250-1bfb-4bb7-a8b3-9df9ed54a311%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20foam%5C%22%3EBest%20foam%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20be%20tricky%20to%20find%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-foam-mattress%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20foam%20mattress%3C%2Fa%3E%20that's%20supportive%20enough%20for%20a%20stomach%20sleeper.%20There's%20this%20connotation%20with%20foam%20that%20your%20body%20will%20sink%20too%20much%2C%20but%20that's%20not%20the%20case%20when%20you%20find%20the%20right%20high-density%20foam%20that%20is%20able%20to%20support%20and%20contour%20your%20body.%20The%20Tempur-Pedic%20ProAdapt%20is%20available%20in%20four%20firmness%20options%20%E2%80%94%20Soft%2C%20Medium%2C%20Medium%20Hybrid%2C%20and%20Firm%20%E2%80%94%20with%20the%20Firm%20being%20an%20optimal%20option%20for%20stomach%20sleepers%20as%20its%20high-density%20foam%20mattress%20keeps%20the%20spine%20aligned.%20Feel%20wise%2C%20you%20can%20expect%20a%20contouring%20surface%20that%20lifts%20your%20hips%20and%20lower%20back.%20According%20to%20Tempur-Pedic%2C%20the%20ProAdapt%20offers%2020%20percent%20more%20pressure%20relief%20thanks%20to%20the%20Tempur-Material%20they%20adapted%20from%20NASA%20to%20be%20more%20conforming%2C%20motion%20absorbing%2C%20durable%2C%20and%20pressure%20relieving.%20This%20is%20something%20that%20would%20benefit%20stomach%20sleepers%20as%20such%20a%20sleep%20position%20can%20put%20pressure%20on%20your%20joints%20and%20muscles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20any%20foam%20mattress%2C%20the%20Tempur-Pedic%20Pro%20Adapt%20excels%20in%20terms%20of%20motion%20isolation.%20Your%20partner%20can%20get%20in%20and%20out%20of%20bed%20or%20change%20sleep%20positions%2C%20and%20you%20likely%20won't%20feel%20it.%20Of%20the%20four%20firmness%20options%2C%20the%20Medium-Hybrid%20will%20have%20the%20best%20edge%20support%2C%20since%20it%20is%20a%20hybrid%20mattress%2C%20but%20our%20tester%20who%20also%20spent%20some%20time%20on%20the%20Firm%20felt%20minimal%20sinkage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20foam%20layers%20of%20the%20Tempur-Pedic%20ProAdapt%20are%20perforated%20for%20airflow%2C%20which%20improves%20breathability.%20Reviewers'%20feedback%20is%20mixed%2C%20but%20it%20seems%20that%20this%20foam%20mattress%20does%20a%20pretty%20good%20job%20of%20regulating%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tempur-Pedic%20Pro%20Adapt%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20expensive%20mattresses%20in%20this%20guide%2C%20so%20it's%20a%20little%20disappointing%20to%20see%20its%2090-night%20trial%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20shortest%20trials%20and%20may%20incur%20a%20shipping%20return%20fee.%20It%20does%2C%20however%2C%20include%20in-home%20set-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Ftempur-pedic-proadapt-mattress-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETempur-Pedic%20ProAdapt%20mattress%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b4537173-2cec-450f-a2e1-5c7dabaf22de%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20back%20pain%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20for%20back%20pain%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESleeping%20on%20your%20stomach%20always%20comes%20with%20the%20risk%20of%20lower%20back%20pain%2C%20especially%20if%20the%20mattress%20isn't%20supportive%20around%20your%20hips.%20If%20back%20pain%20is%20your%20biggest%20concern%2C%20the%20Bear%20Elite%20Hybrid%20is%20an%20ideal%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%2014-inch%20mattress%20comes%20in%20three%20firmness%20level%20options%20%E2%80%94%20soft%2C%20medium%2C%20and%20firm%20%E2%80%94%20and%20having%20tested%20the%20medium%20option%2C%20I%20can%20say%20that%20it%20did%20a%20great%20job%20in%20pressure%20relief%2C%20especially%20along%20my%20lower%20back.%20This%20has%20to%20do%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20mattress%20has%20a%20zoned%20coil%20system%20to%20relieve%20pressure%20points.%20High%20gauge%20coils%20are%20placed%20down%20the%20center%20for%20lumbar%20support.%20The%20coil%20system%20and%20memory%20foam%20(that's%20infused%20with%20copper%20with%20antimicrobial%20properties)%20work%20in%20tandem%20to%20eliminate%20lower%20back%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bear%20elite%20hybrid%20mattress%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6797ff357bb3f854015a91c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20medium%20Bear%20Elite%20Hybrid%20has%20a%20has%20a%20zoned%20coil%20system%20to%20relieve%20pressure%20points%20and%20helps%20alleviate%20back%20pain.%3Cp%3EBrendan%20Griffiths%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20can%20manage%20the%20additional%20%24195%2C%20add%20the%20Celliant-infused%20cooling%20cover.%20Not%20only%20is%20it%20plush%20enough%20to%20put%20you%20to%20sleep%20in%20seconds%20(as%20it%20did%20with%20me)%2C%20but%20it%20assists%20with%20the%20cooling%20features%20of%20this%20hybrid%20mattress.%20I%20tested%20the%20mattress%20in%20July%20in%20Texas%20and%20never%20once%20woke%20up%20warm%20or%20sweaty%20thanks%20to%20the%20cover.%20The%20temperature%20regulation%20combined%20with%20the%20mattress'%20support%20and%20nestling%20cover%20will%20make%20for%20a%20lovely%20night%20of%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20hybrid%20mattress%2C%20the%20Bear%20Elite%20Hybrid%20does%20a%20great%20job%20isolating%20motion%2C%20making%20it%20a%20good%20choice%20for%20couples.%20The%20edge%20support%20is%20most%20impressive%20along%20the%20sides%20of%20the%20mattress%20rather%20than%20at%20the%20foot%20of%20the%20bed%20or%20the%20corners.%20I%20wouldn't%20let%20this%20affect%20your%20decision%20to%20try%20it%2C%20especially%20since%20this%20mattress%20has%20a%20120-night%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECheck%20out%20our%20guide%20for%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-mattress-for-back-pain%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20best%20mattresses%20for%20back%20pain%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cu%3E.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bcdfef53-e34d-4c3c-94bc-3ab42377f302%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20extra-firm%5C%22%3EBest%20extra-firm%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20name%20like%20%26quot%3BPlank%2C%26quot%3B%20it's%20no%20wonder%20that%20the%20Plank%20Firm%20by%20Brooklyn%20Bedding%20is%20our%20extra%20firm%20pick.%20The%20only%20thing%20firmer%20would%20be%20sleeping%20on%20the%20actual%20floor.%20What%20makes%20this%20surprisingly%20affordable%20mattress%20special%20is%20that%20it's%20flippable.%20One%20side%20of%20the%20mattress%20has%20an%20extra-firm%20feel%20(marked%20at%20a%2010%20on%20the%2010-point%20firmness%20scale)%20while%20the%20other%20side%20is%20medium-firm%20(marked%20at%20an%208).%20If%20you%20have%20a%20partner%20who%20can't%20sleep%20on%20their%20stomach%2C%20you%20might%20need%20to%20flip%20the%20mattress%20to%20the%20medium-firm%20side%2C%20though%20for%20couples%20to%20be%20comfortable%20on%20a%20mattress%20this%20firm%2C%20you'll%20hopefully%20want%20to%20both%20have%20an%20appreciation%20for%20firm%20mattresses.%20Stomach%20sleepers%20should%20be%20able%20to%20sleep%20on%20either%20side%20of%20this%20mattress%2C%20as%20it's%20sure%20to%20keep%20their%20spine%20aligned%20and%20their%20hips%20and%20lower%20back%20supported.%20It%20will%20likely%20be%20too%20hard%20on%20pressure%20points%20for%20side%20and%20some%20back%20sleepers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22plank%20mattress%20with%20a%20bowling%20ball%20on%20top%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66df68e0a0ff598b2665fe8f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBoth%20sides%20of%20the%20Plank%20are%20made%20up%20of%20firm%20and%20extra-firm%20high%20density%20memory%20foam%3B%20the%20bed%20is%20as%20close%20to%20sleeping%20on%20a%20table%20as%20you%20can%20get.%3Cp%3EJaclyn%20Turner%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20breathability%2C%20we're%20pretty%20impressed%20by%20the%20temperature%20regulation%2C%20especially%20considering%20it's%20an%20all-foam%20mattress.%20Even%20so%2C%20hot%20sleepers%20might%20want%20to%20upgrade%20to%20the%20GlacioTex%20Cooling%20Cover%20for%20an%20even%20cooler%20sleep%20experience.%20Just%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20the%20cover%20can%20only%20be%20placed%20on%20the%20extra%20firm%20side%20of%20the%20mattress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20memory%20foam%20mattress%2C%20you%20can%20expect%20better-than-average%20motion%20isolation.%20Your%20partner%20won't%20wake%20you%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night.%20Surprisingly%2C%20the%20edge%20support%20is%20better%20than%20most%20memory%20foam%20mattresses%2C%20most%20likely%20due%20in%20part%20to%20the%20extremely%20high%20density%20foams.%20Perhaps%20the%20biggest%20drawback%20to%20this%20extra%20firm%20mattress%20is%20that%20returns%20incur%20a%20%2499%20fee%20if%20you%20decide%20it's%20not%20the%20bed%20for%20you.%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbrooklyn-bedding-plank-firm-mattress-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPlank%20Firm%20Mattress%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2201923ac6-4bd5-4dab-8370-f85220acd098%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20cooling%5C%22%3EBest%20cooling%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFoam%20mattresses%20aren't%20typically%20known%20for%20their%20cooling%20capabilities%2C%20which%20is%20what%20makes%20the%20PurpleFlex%20Mattress%20so%20special.%20In%20addition%20to%20a%20base%20support%20foam%20and%20edge%20support%20foam%2C%20this%20mattress%20is%20outfitted%20with%20Purple's%20unique%20GelFlex%20Grid%2C%20which%20is%20made%20of%20an%20ultra-responsive%20and%20pressure-relieving%20proprietary%20Hyper-Elastic%20Polymer%20arranged%20in%20a%20repeating%20geometric%20structure.%20It%20dissipates%20heat%20so%20thoroughly%20that%20I%20actually%20got%20cold%20sleeping%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night.%20It's%20the%20only%20mattress%20I've%20ever%20tested%20that%20had%20me%20sleeping%20in%20sweatpants%20and%20a%20hoodie%2C%20which%20is%20why%20I%20rate%20it%20highly%20among%20our%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-cooling-mattress%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20best%20cooling%20mattresses.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221659%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20PurpleFlex%20Mattress%20is%20displayed%20in%20a%20bedroom.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669eb9852d66759f66fd127e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221244%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPurple's%20responsive%20and%20contouring%20GelFlex%20Grid%20also%20helps%20dissipate%20heat%20and%20promotes%20air%20flow%2C%20which%20is%20a%20plus%20for%20hot%20sleepers.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20other%20foam%20mattresses%2C%20the%20PurpleFlex%20Mattress%20excels%20in%20motion%20isolation%20capabilities.%20To%20test%20this%2C%20I%20placed%20a%20wine%20glass%20in%20the%20center%20of%20the%20mattress%20and%20dropped%20a%2015%20pound%20dumbbell%20four%2C%2010%2C%20and%2025%20inches%20away.%20The%20glass%20only%20wobbled%20slightly%20but%20never%20fell%20over.%20I%20also%20had%20a%20friend%20get%20on%20and%20off%20the%20mattress%20and%20switch%20sleep%20positions%20and%20I%20couldn't%20feel%20them%20move.%20This%20leads%20me%20to%20say%20that%20you%20won't%20wake%20up%20when%20your%20fidgety%20partner%20turns%20in%20their%20sleep%20or%20gets%20up%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20reinforced%20edges%2C%20I%20found%20the%20edge%20support%20to%20be%20lacking.%20You're%20not%20going%20to%20fall%20off%20the%20edge%20as%20you%20sleep%2C%20but%20sitting%20on%20the%20sides%20of%20the%208-inch%20mattress%20will%20have%20you%20sinking%20down%20further%20than%20you%20might%20like.%20Where%20I%20would%20label%20the%20edge%20support%20as%20good%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fpurpleflex-mattress-review%23edge-support%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20another%20Business%20Insider%20reviewer%3C%2Fa%3E%20rated%20it%20as%20great%20because%20when%20they%20laid%20on%20the%20mattress%20with%20their%20shoulders%20aligned%20to%20the%20edge%20and%20slowly%20rolled%20off%20the%20bed%2C%20they%20made%20it%20past%2045%20degrees%20before%20having%20to%20catch%20their%20fall.%20It%20also%20only%20sunk%20down%20three%20inches%2C%20which%20is%20above%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20importantly%2C%20the%20PurpleFlex%20Mattress%20has%20a%20medium-firm%20to%20firm%20feel%2C%20making%20it%20well-suited%20to%20stomach%20and%20back%20sleepers.%20I'd%20rate%20it%20a%207.5%20out%20of%2010%20on%20the%20firmness%20scale.%20The%20surface%20is%20springy%20and%20even%20though%20it%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20sleeping%20on%20top%20of%20the%20mattress%2C%20the%20foam%20slightly%20contoured%20around%20my%20body.%20If%20all%20that%20doesn't%20convince%20you%20to%20buy%20the%20PurpleFlex%20Mattress%2C%20perhaps%20the%20price%20will.%20It's%20Purple's%20most%20affordable%20offering%2C%20and%20when%20on%20sale%2C%20a%20queen-size%20mattress%20can%20go%20for%20less%20than%20%241%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fpurpleflex-mattress-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPurpleFlex%20Mattress%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2286784f0c-8c4c-47d3-a5a7-89400c77067b%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20couples%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20couples%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECouples%20can't%20go%20wrong%20with%20the%20Awara%20Premier%20Luxury%20Hybrid%20Mattress.%20This%20organic%20hybrid%20mattress%20has%20four%20inches%20of%20GOLS%20%26amp%3B%20FSC-certified%20organic%20latex%20and%20a%20cover%20quilted%20with%20New%20Zealand%20organic%20wool%20under%20a%20rayon%20blend%20made%20from%20bamboo.%20Comfort-wise%2C%20I'd%20describe%20the%20Awara%20Premier%20Luxury%20Hybrid%20Mattress%20as%20medium-firm.%20The%20top%20layer%20is%20cozy%20and%20soft%20while%20providing%20support%20along%20the%20hips%20and%20lower%20back%2C%20marking%20it%20as%20an%20ideal%20option%20for%20stomach%20and%20back%20sleepers.%20It%20could%20potentially%20be%20suitable%20to%20your%20side%20sleeping%20partner%20too%2C%20as%20there%20is%20a%20slight%20give%20to%20the%20surface.%20With%20a%20year-long%20trial%20with%20free%20returns%2C%20couples%20can%20make%20sure%20that%20it%20fits%20their%20different%20sleep%20styles.%20Edge%20support%20is%20impressive%20along%20the%20sides%2C%20more%20so%20than%20the%20foot%20of%20the%20bed%2C%20meaning%20if%20you%20have%20a%20partner%20who%20sprawls%20over%20from%20their%20half%20of%20the%20bed%2C%20you%20can%20feel%20secure%20if%20you%20get%20pushed%20to%20the%20edge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20side%20shot%20of%20the%20awara%20mattress%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671a9880a0a0cc14f223b0e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECouples%20or%20combination%20sleepers%20with%20different%20sleep%20preferences%20will%20like%20the%20Awara's%20medium%20feel%20that%20appeals%20to%20all%20sleep%20types.%20It%20also%20has%20excellent%20edge%20support%20and%20decent%20motion%20isolation.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20running%20a%20variety%20of%20tests%2C%20I%20came%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20the%20motion%20isolation%20is%20fairly%20good.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20I%20think%20most%20couples%20would%20be%20satisfied%20with%20the%20mattress'%20motion%20isolation%2C%20but%20they%20may%20feel%20a%20slight%20bit%20of%20movement%20when%20one%20partner%20moves%20during%20the%20night.%20At%20the%20least%2C%20the%20surface%20is%20bouncy%20%E2%80%94%20a%20pro%20for%20sex.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhere%20it%20succeeds%20most%20is%20in%20temperature%20regulation.%20The%20Awara%20Premier%20Luxury%20Hybrid%20Mattress%20won't%20make%20you%20and%20your%20partner%20feel%20cool%2C%20but%20it%20will%20keep%20both%20your%20body%20temperatures%20neutral%20throughout%20the%20night.%20This%20is%20of%20no%20surprise%2C%20as%20it's%20something%20that%20organic%20hybrid%20mattresses%20do%20exceptionally%20well.%20Considering%20the%20organic%20materials%20and%20the%20lifetime%20warranty%2C%20the%20Awara%20Premier%20Luxury%20Hybrid%20Mattress%20is%20a%20solid%20mattress%20buy%20for%20couples.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fawara-premier-luxury-hybrid-mattress-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAwara%20Premier%20Luxury%20Hybrid%20Mattress%20review.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2258b8a0ef-b918-4700-b466-dc99db930a97%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2208dda325-af97-43af-944c-61d15190638a%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Type%5C%22%3EType%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20not%20a%20single%20mattress%20type%20that's%20best%20for%20stomach%20sleepers%2C%20however%2C%20most%20stomach%20sleepers%20tend%20to%20gravitate%20toward%20hybrid%20and%20innerspring%20mattresses%20because%20they're%20usually%20on%20the%20firmer%20side%2C%20thus%20offering%20the%20kind%20of%20support%20that%20stomach%20sleepers%20need.%20Despite%20that%2C%20we've%20included%20a%20latex%20foam%20mattress%20as%20our%20number%20one%20pick%20and%20quite%20a%20few%20foam%20mattresses%20on%20this%20list%2C%20proving%20that%20there%20are%20no%20hard%20and%20fast%20rules%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fhow-to-choose-a-mattress%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echoosing%20a%20mattress%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222446d804-93d9-4ffa-b163-aa84b62098f5%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Firmness%5C%22%3EFirmness%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EStomach%20sleepers%20will%20find%20better%20sleep%20and%20pressure%20relief%20with%20a%20firmer%20mattress.%20On%20a%2010-point%20firmness%20scale%2C%20the%20mattress%20should%20be%20no%20less%20than%20a%206.%20This%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20a%20mattress%20with%20an%208%20or%20a%2010%20on%20the%20firmness%20scale%20will%20suit%20you%20better.%20In%20fact%2C%20that%20might%20be%20too%20firm%20for%20some%20(and%20not%20for%20others).%20Keep%20an%20eye%20out%20for%20mattresses%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Bmedium-firm%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bfirm%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20they'll%20be%20better%20suited%20to%20your%20sleep%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20weigh%20over%20250%20pounds%2C%20may%20find%20medium-firm%20mattresses%20to%20be%20too%20soft%20or%20not%20provide%20the%20same%20support%20as%20they%20would%20to%20someone%20who%20weighs%20less.%20In%20that%20case%2C%20an%20extra%20firm%20or%20firm%20mattress%20with%20a%20higher%20rating%20on%20the%20firmness%20scale%20would%20be%20a%20better%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2211fe9342-d0d9-43b8-bfd3-0a30efadd303%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Spinal%20alignment%2FPressure%20Relief%5C%22%3ESpinal%20alignment%20and%20pressure%20relief%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20all%20types%20of%20sleepers%20need%20to%20keep%20spinal%20alignment%20and%20pressure%20relief%20in%20mind%20when%20looking%20for%20a%20mattress%2C%20it's%20especially%20important%20for%20stomach%20sleepers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20sleeping%2C%20the%20spine%20and%20pelvis%20should%20remain%20in%20a%20neutral%20position%20to%20reduce%20joint%20pressure%20and%20stress%20on%20associated%20musculature%2C%26quot%3B%20advises%20Dr.%20Kevin%20Lees%2C%20D.C.%2C%20Director%20of%20Chiropractic%20Operations%20at%20The%20Joint%20Chiropractic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20why%20medium-firm%20to%20firm%20mattresses%20are%20the%20better%20choice%20for%20stomach%20sleepers.%20They%20do%20a%20better%20job%20at%20aligning%20your%20spine%20by%20lifting%20your%20hips%20and%20lower%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a8fe42ab-b964-43c1-b71a-3d8df2805af3%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Breathability%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBreathability%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20shopping%20for%20a%20mattress%2C%20it's%20incredibly%20important%20to%20consider%20a%20breathable%20or%20temperature%20regulating%20mattress.%20A%20mattress%20that%20does%20a%20poor%20job%20at%20dissipating%20heat%20is%20one%20that%20will%20disrupt%20your%20sleep%20causing%20you%20to%20wake%20up%20due%20to%20the%20heat%20or%20because%20you're%20sweating%20(or%20both).%20You%20don't%20necessarily%20need%20a%20%26quot%3Bcooling%20mattress%2C%26quot%3B%20though%20it's%20definitely%20something%20that%20hot%20sleepers%20or%20those%20who%20tend%20to%20sweat%20easily%20might%20want%20to%20consider.%20We've%20tested%20plenty%20of%20mattresses%20that%20are%20designed%20to%20keep%20a%20sleeper's%20temperature%20%26quot%3Bneutral%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20can%20ensure%20a%20great%20sleep%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2273e25a9b-59eb-4341-a149-fc6e8f5a68a0%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Motion%20Isolation%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMotion%20Isolation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20share%20a%20bed%20with%20another%20person%2C%20then%20you'll%20want%20a%20mattress%20with%20great%20motion%20isolation%20capabilities%20because%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20awoken%20when%20your%20partner%20moves%20or%20gets%20in%20and%20out%20of%20bed.%20Typically%20foam%20mattresses%20do%20better%20than%20hybrid%20mattresses%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20motion%20isolation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22937eee65-b2be-4c3f-bd92-a0d900014661%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Edge%20Support%5C%22%3EEdge%20Support%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EEdge%20support%20can%20be%20important%20to%20the%20mattress'%20structural%20integrity%2C%20ensuring%20that%20it%20lasts%20longer.%20It%20also%20extends%20the%20sleep%20surface%20area%20and%20can%20make%20getting%20in%20and%20out%20of%20bed%20a%20lot%20easier.%20Firmer%20mattresses%20and%20hybrid%20mattresses%20tend%20to%20have%20better%20edge%20support%20than%20other%20mattresses%20because%20of%20the%20use%20of%20firmer%20materials%2C%20however%2C%20that's%20not%20always%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ff728684-163b-4e66-a45a-ecd2faf89bc6%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Company%20policies%20(trial%2C%20return%20policy%2C%20warranty)%5C%22%3ECompany%20policies%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ECompany%20policies%20may%20not%20seem%20that%20important%2C%20but%20they%20can%20make%20a%20big%20difference.%20Regardless%20if%20you%20purchase%20your%20bed%20online%20versus%20a%20store%2C%20a%20lengthy%20sleep%20will%20help%20you%20determine%20if%20the%20mattress%20is%20right%20for%20you.%20This%20is%20where%20the%20sleep%20trial%20policy%20comes%20in.%20Most%20mattresses%20offer%20at%20least%20100%20nights%20to%20test%20a%20mattress%2C%20though%20some%20offer%20up%20to%20a%20year.%20Always%20check%20to%20see%20if%20the%20brand%20will%20charge%20you%20a%20fee%20to%20return%20the%20mattress%20if%20it's%20not%20a%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEqually%20as%20important%20is%20the%20warranty.%20Ten-year%20warranties%20are%20most%20common%2C%20because%20most%20mattress%20materials%20break%20down%20after%2010%20years.%20Some%20brands%20are%20now%20offering%20lifetime%20warranties%2C%20which%20could%20save%20you%20considerable%20amounts%20of%20money%20in%20the%20future.%20Always%20read%20the%20fine%20print%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20warranties.%20For%20instance%2C%20there%20are%20some%20lifetime%20warranties%20broken%20down%20into%20decades%20and%20have%20fees%20associated%20after%20the%2020-year%20mark%2C%20or%20only%20apply%20to%20the%20original%20purchasers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222f96c920-fa7a-4efb-8981-f6c6d3628f65%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20chose%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20we%20chose%20the%20best%20mattresses%20for%20stomach%20sleepers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20testing%20mattresses%20since%202021%20for%20various%20outlets.%20As%20of%20now%2C%20I've%20tested%20over%2020%20mattresses%2C%20including%20my%20latest%20with%20Business%20Insider%E2%80%94the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fawara-premier-luxury-hybrid-mattress-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Awara%20Premier%20Luxury%20Hybrid%20Mattress%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20buying%20guide%2C%20I%20utilized%20my%20own%20testing%20experience%20and%20that%20of%20my%20fellow%20Business%20Insider%20reviewers%20to%20determine%20the%20best%20fit%20for%20each%20category.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20testing%20mattresses%20for%20Business%20Insider%2C%20we%20go%20beyond%20the%20comfort%20and%20feel%20of%20a%20mattress%2C%20and%20look%20at%20other%20key%20characteristics%20like%20edhe%20support%2C%20motion%20isolation%2C%20and%20temperature%20regulation.%20We%20also%20examine%20the%20various%20policies%20related%20to%20mattresses%20and%20determine%20whether%20the%20price%20matches%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20mattress%20at%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELearn%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fhow-we-test-mattresses%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20we%20test%20mattresses.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dcfebbc5-6120-4bc6-9fc8-e69d5702392e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMattress%20for%20stomach%20sleepers%20FAQs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20type%20of%20mattress%20is%20best%20for%20stomach%20sleepers%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20provided%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20mattress%20types%20for%20stomach%20sleepers%20in%20this%20guide.%20Whether%20you%20prefer%20foam%20or%20hybrid%20mattresses%2C%20we've%20got%20you%20covered.%20That%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BInnerspring%20mattresses%20often%20have%20the%20firmest%20feel%2C%20but%20a%20hybrid%20or%20foam%20mattress%20may%20help%20avoid%20pressure%20points%20over%20the%20pelvis%20or%20arms%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr.%20Lees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20much%20as%20we%20want%20to%20say%20that%20one%20mattress%20type%20is%20better%20than%20another%2C%20they%20all%20have%20their%20benefits%2C%20even%20to%20stomach%20sleepers.%20However%2C%20if%20you%20can%20find%20a%20firm%20mattress%20that%20you%20like%2C%20you're%20likely%20to%20have%20a%20better%20sleep%20experience%20in%20the%20long%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EIs%20a%20soft%20or%20firm%20mattress%20better%20for%20stomach%20sleepers%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EStomach%20sleepers%20should%20invest%20invest%20in%20a%20mattress%20on%20the%20firmer%20side%2C%20and%20should%20at%20least%20be%20of%20medium%20firmness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20mattress%20that%20is%20too%20soft%20may%20allow%20the%20stomach%20and%20hips%20to%20sink%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20spinal%20stress%20with%20increased%20neck%20extension%20or%20an%20increased%20lower%20back%20curve%2C%26quot%3B%20explains%20Dr.%20Lees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20type%20of%20mattress%20should%20you%20get%20if%20your%20a%20combination%20sleeper%20and%20lay%20on%20your%20stomach%20and%20side%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20combo%20sleeper%2C%20I've%20found%20that%20hybrid%20mattresses%20are%20usually%20better%20for%20stomach%20and%20back%20sleepers.%20Foam%20mattresses%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20they're%20made%20with%20latex%20or%20memory%20foam%20%E2%80%94%20typically%20benefit%20side%20and%20stomach%20sleepers.%20All%20that%20to%20say%2C%20I've%20definitely%20slept%20on%20my%20stomach%20and%20side%20on%20various%20hybrid%20mattresses%20like%20the%20Awara%20Premier%20Luxury%20Hybrid.%20It%20really%20depends%20on%20your%20weight%2C%20body%20structure%2C%20and%20how%20the%20surface%20of%20a%20mattress%20feels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EIs%20it%20healthy%20to%20sleep%20on%20your%20stomach%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20comfortable%20as%20it%20is%20for%20you%20to%20sleep%20on%20your%20stomach%2C%20it%20might%20not%20be%20the%20healthiest%20sleep%20position.%20According%20to%20Dr.%20Lees%2C%20%26quot%3BStomach%20sleeping%20can%20stress%20the%20upper%20back%2C%20neck%2C%20and%20lower%20back.%20Stomach%20sleepers%20must%20turn%20their%20heads%20to%20the%20side%20when%20sleeping%20to%20breathe%2C%20and%20this%20rotation%20and%20extension%20can%20cause%20tension%20and%20pressure%20on%20the%20muscles%20and%20joints%20in%20the%20upper%20back%20and%20neck.%20Stomach%20sleeping%20can%20increase%20the%20natural%20curve%20of%20the%20lower%20back.%20This%20added%20stress%20can%20cause%20joint%20inflammation%20and%20pain.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20all%20that%20wasn't%20enough%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20long-term%20effects%20of%20stomach%20sleeping%20could%20lead%20to%20headaches%2C%20nerve%20compression%2C%20and%20osteoarthritis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EShould%20stomach%20sleepers%20sleep%20with%20a%20pillow%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EPillows%20aren't%20a%20necessity%20for%20stomach%20sleepers%2C%20however%2C%20if%20you%20want%20to%20sleep%20with%20a%20pillow%2C%20%E2%80%94%20we%20recommend%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-pillow%23best-for-stomach-sleepers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EParachute's%20down%20alternative%20pillow%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20soft%20%E2%80%94%20there%20are%20some%20things%20to%20consider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20stomach%20sleepers%20might%20prefer%20no%20pillow%20at%20all.%20If%20using%20a%20pillow%2C%20it%20should%20be%20made%20of%20soft%2C%20breathable%20material%20and%20thin%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr.%20Lees.%20%26quot%3BToo%20much%20loft%20or%20thickness%20can%20cause%20the%20neck%20to%20be%20pushed%20backward%20at%20an%20awkward%20angle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20can%20you%20make%20a%20mattress%20firmer%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20make%20your%20mattress%20firmer%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20invest%20in%20a%20firm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-mattress-topper%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emattress%20topper%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20latex%20or%20high-density%20foam%20topper%20is%20your%20best%20bet%2C%20though%20that's%20not%20to%20say%20that%20a%20memory%20foam%20topper%20couldn't%20firm%20up%20your%20mattress%20too.%20For%20instance%2C%20I%20tested%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D648bc9ad334b60fd325ae96a26ad3c030068eefb