3E%3Cem%3EChinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20(centre)%20stands%20with%20leaders%20from%20African%20countries%20at%20the%20meeting%20of%20the%20Forum%20on%20China-Africa%20Cooperation%2C%20in%20Beijing%20in%20September%202024.%20(AFP)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsmall%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENatural-%20and%20human-resource-rich%20Africa%20has%20seen%20many%20a%20geopolitical%20storm.%20It%20has%20suffered%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20exploitation%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20its%20colonial%20and%20neo-colonial%20masters%2C%20as%20well%20as%20that%20of%20its%20own%20power-%20and%20pelf-hungry%20leaders.%20Poverty%20and%20underdevelopment%20still%20are%20the%20biggest%20bane%20of%20the%20region%2C%20irrespective%20of%20who%20holds%20the%20reins.%20Whether%20it's%20military%20leaders%20and%20juntas%20or%20the%20crafty%20politicians%20they%20try%20to%20overthrow%2C%20the%20slogans%20and%20the%20promises%20remain%20the%20same.%20Many%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20I%20was%20in%20Nigeria%20and%20we%20covered%20several%20African%20countries%2C%20it%20was%20a%20general%20belief%20that%20every%20officer%20of%20the%20rank%20of%20Colonel%20and%20above%20harboured%20a%20dream%20to%20be%20the%20Head%20of%20State%20or%20government%20someday.%20Coups%20were%20common.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20also%20a%20fact%20that%20it%20was%20President%20Olu%E1%B9%A3%E1%BA%B9gun%20%E1%BB%8Cbasanj%E1%BB%8D%2C%20an%20army%20man%2C%20who%20ushered%20in%20democracy%20in%20Nigeria.%20That%20his%20position%20of%20power%20failed%20to%20save%20him%20is%20a%20different%20story%20though.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20times%2C%20West%20Africa%20and%20Sahel%2C%20and%20many%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20continent%2C%20have%20not%20only%20witnessed%20the%20overthrow%20of%20regimes%20by%20military%20coups%2C%20but%20also%20the%20wiping%20out%20of%20the%20last%20remaining%20footprints%20of%20erstwhile%20colonial%20powers.%20The%20French%20are%20the%20biggest%20losers%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrance%20Losing%20Its%20Edge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20number%20of%20francophone%20countries%20have%20been%20severing%20their%20French%20connection%2C%20and%20the%20French%2C%20despite%20their%20last-ditch%20efforts%2C%20haven't%20been%20able%20to%20salvage%20the%20situation.%20Last%20year%2C%20Niger%2C%20Mali%20and%20Burkina%20Faso%20asked%20the%20French%20and%20Americans%20to%20leave%20their%20territories%20and%20cut%20off%20all%20ties%20as%20they%20moved%20to%20build%20closer%20ones%20with%20Russia%20and%20China.%20When%20big%20brother%20Nigeria%20and%20the%20Economic%20Community%20of%20West%20African%20States%20(ECOWAS)%20tried%20to%20intervene%2C%20not%20only%20did%20the%20three%20countries%20put%20up%20a%20defiant%20protest%2C%20but%20they%20also%20created%20their%20own%20trilateral%2C%20displaying%20a%20kind%20of%20macho-nationalism%20against%20their%20own%20African%20brothers.%20Despite%20action%20by%20the%20African%20Union%20(AU)%20and%20the%20ECOWAS%2C%20the%20three%20countries%20have%20refused%20to%20yield%2C%20forcing%20regional%20institutions%20to%20take%20a%20more%20inclusive%20approach.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChad%20and%20Cote%20d'Ivoire%20have%20also%20pushed%20for%20a%20withdrawal%20of%20French%20troops%20and%20severance%20of%20ties.%20In%20the%201980s%2C%20when%20I%20was%20serving%20in%20Abidjan%2C%20Cote%20d'Ivoire%20was%20the%20show%20window%20of%20the%20French%20in%20Africa%3B%20according%20to%20some%20estimates%2C%20nearly%2093%25%20of%20the%20decision-making%20was%20done%20mostly%20by%20the%20French%20advisor%20or%20the%20%E2%80%98Directeur%20de%20cabinet'%20in%20a%20particular%20Ministry.%20Their%20currency%2C%20the%20French%20Franc%2C%20was%20the%20mainstay%20of%20their%20intervention%20and%20rule%2C%20and%20the%20French%20rapid%20deployment%20forces%20were%20stationed%20there%20to%20secure%20the%20Presidency.%20In%20fact%2C%20at%20the%20time%2C%20a%20French%20Colonel%20from%20Pondicherry%20headed%20the%20contingent.%20All%20the%20accounting%20in%20their%20embassies%20was%20mainly%20allotted%20to%20Indian-origin%20officials%20from%20Pondicherry.%20True%2C%20this%20arrangement%20was%20too%20good%20to%20last%2C%20but%20compared%20to%20their%20British%20counterparts%2C%20the%20French%20colonisers%20were%20smarter%20and%20did%20not%20avoid%20social%20mixing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUltimately%20though%2C%20the%20Africans%20paid%20dearly%20for%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%98management'%20of%20the%20region%2C%20and%20the%20discontent%20finally%20ignited%20a%20revolt%20against%20French%20establishments%20in%20their%20countries%2C%20embers%20of%20which%20continue%20to%20burn.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmerica%20Tries%20To%20Catch%20Up%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20month%20before%20demitting%20office%2C%20former%20US%20President%2C%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20had%20hosted%20the%20US-Africa%20Summit%20and%20made%20his%20last%20visit%20to%20Angola%2C%20emphasising%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20Lobito%20corridor.%20Aimed%20at%20countering%20Chinese%20influence%20in%20the%20region%2C%20the%20US-backed%20project%20will%20connect%20critical%20minerals%20mines%20in%20Zambia%20and%20Congo%20with%20the%20Lobito%20port%20in%20Angola.%20Even%20Trump%20is%20expected%20to%20focus%20more%20on%20Africa%20in%20his%20current%20term%2C%20no%20matter%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20had%20called%20the%20place%20a%20%E2%80%9Cshithole%E2%80%9D%20in%20his%20last.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20policy%20in%20Africa%20is%20largely%20driven%20by%20concerns%20about%20countering%20China%20and%20Russia%20in%20the%20region.%20As%20such%2C%20it%20tends%20to%20ignore%20the%20interests%20of%20Africans%20in%20general%20and%20serves%20only%20its%20own%20geopolitical%20objectives.%20The%20disenchantment%20with%20Americans%20at%20the%20grassroots%20is%2C%20hence%2C%20natural%2C%20and%20quite%20visible.%20Memories%20of%20the%20West's%20historical%20excesses%20in%20the%20region%20during%20the%20colonial%20era%20have%20anyway%20led%20to%20a%20credibility%20crisis%2C%20which%2C%20by%20default%2C%20lends%20a%20certain%20acceptability%20to%20both%20Moscow%20and%20Beijing%2C%20both%20of%20which%20stay%20heavily%20engaged%20through%20their%20Africa%20summits%20and%20direct%20outreach%20and%20military%20and%20material%20support%20to%20all%20kinds%20of%20regimes.%20They%20do%20it%20without%20any%20compunction%20or%20value%20proposition%2C%20unlike%20the%20West%2C%20whose%20overly%20prescriptive%20behaviour%2C%20policies%20and%20conditionalities%20evoke%20anger%20and%20disappointment%20both%20at%20the%20popular%20and%20leadership%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20US%20did%20launch%20the%20%E2%80%98Prosper%20Africa'%20initiative%20in%202019%2C%20it's%20Russia's%20Wagner%20Group%E2%80%94now%20rechristened%20African%20Corps%E2%80%94that%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20major%20tool%20for%20wielding%20influence%20in%20several%20African%20countries.%20Trump%20appears%20to%20be%20rocking%20that%20boat%3A%20he%20threatened%20to%20cut%20the%20funding%20to%20South%20Africa%20over%20allegations%20that%20the%20latter%20was%20confiscating%20land%E2%80%94most%20private%20farmland%20in%20the%20country%20is%20still%20owned%20by%20Whites%E2%80%94and%20%E2%80%9Ctreating%20certain%20classes%20of%20people%20badly%E2%80%9D.%20Perhaps%20what%20the%20US%20President%20didn't%20realise%20was%20that%20this%20year%2C%20South%20Africa%20is%20also%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20G20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EChina%20In%20A%20Consistency%20Loop%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20China's%20Foreign%20Minister%2C%20Wang%20Yi%2C%20has%20made%20it%20a%20practice%20since%201991%20to%20start%20the%20New%20Year%20by%20visiting%20several%20African%20countries.%20This%20January%E2%80%94his%2057th%20trip%E2%80%94he%20was%20in%20Namibia%2C%20the%20Republic%20of%20Congo%2C%20Chad%20and%20Nigeria.%20While%20he%20nearly%20missed%20the%20coup%20in%20Chad%2C%20Congo%20was%20facing%20its%20own%20moment%20of%20reckoning%2C%20thanks%20to%20Rwanda-backed%20M23%20rebels.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeijing%20is%20also%20keen%20on%20expanding%20its%20Global%20Security%20Initiative%20(GSI)%20in%20Africa.%20It%20has%20chosen%20Nigeria%20for%20a%20closer%20partnership%20as%20it%20is%20the%20biggest%20and%20richest%20country%20in%20the%20region.%20China%20is%20a%20major%20supplier%20of%20weapons%20and%20military%20equipment%20to%20Nigeria%20and%20is%20also%20working%20to%20initiate%20joint%20manufacturing%20of%20defence%20armaments%20in%20the%20country.%20Its%20infrastructure%20projects%20range%20from%20ports%20(62%20projects%20across%20Africa)%20and%20roads%20to%20strategic%20connectivity%20and%20securing%20the%20supplies%20of%20critical%20minerals%20and%20resources%2C%20including%20in%20the%20Horn%20of%20Africa%2C%20where%20it%20already%20has%20a%20base.%20It%20is%20also%20building%20a%20new%20headquarters%20for%20the%20ECOWAS.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20China-Africa%20Forum%20Summits%20(FOCAC)%20have%20been%20held%20regularly%20too%2C%20the%20last%20being%20in%20September%202024.%20It%20has%2010%20programmes%20ranging%20from%20industrialisation%20and%20expansion%20of%20Chinese%20free%20trade%20zones%20to%20police%20and%20military%20cooperation.%20Under%20these%2C%20Beijing%20has%20been%20able%20to%20keep%20the%20contact%20alive%20at%20the%20highest%20level%20and%20course-correct%20wherever%20required%2C%20especially%20as%20other%20competitors%20try%20to%20counter%20it%20and%20expose%20the%20Chinese%20debt%20trap%20diplomacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%20last%20year%2C%20the%20People's%20Liberation%20Army%20(PLA)%20Navy%20hosted%20West%20African%20defence%20chiefs%20in%20Shanghai%20for%20the%20Second%20Symposium%2C%20briefing%20them%20on%20the%20security%20situation%20in%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Guinea%2C%20an%20area%20of%20deep%20interest%20for%20the%20CCP.%20This%20year%2C%20China%20reportedly%20plans%20to%20train%206%2C000%20African%20senior%20officers%2C%20500%20junior%20officers%20and%201%2C000%20law%20enforcement%20officers.%20Its%20African%20partners%20are%20also%20not%20averse%20to%20either%20the%20new%20Chinese%20troika%20of%20the%20Global%20Security%20Initiative%20(GSI)%2C%20the%20Global%20Civilization%20Initiative%20(GCI)%20and%20the%20Global%20Development%20Initiative%20(GDI)%2C%20or%20the%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%20(BRI).%20As%20such%2C%20China%20has%20stayed%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20list%20of%20Africa's%20trading%20partners%20for%20the%20last%2015%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERussia%20On%20A%20Roll%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%2C%20too%2C%20has%20been%20reviving%20and%20expanding%20its%20footprint%20in%20Africa%20through%20bilateral%20exchanges.%20It%20has%20managed%20to%20win%20some%20support%20through%20the%20food%20assistance%20and%20fuel%20security%20it%20has%20extended%20to%20the%20region%20despite%20Western%20pressure%20and%20sanctions.%20The%20Wagner%20groups%20(now%20renamed)%20have%20filled%20the%20external%20gaps%20rather%20quickly%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20Sahel%2C%20Sahara%20and%20northern%20and%20central%20Africa.%20Like%20China%2C%20the%20Russians%2C%20too%2C%20offer%20support%20for%20their%20favoured%20actors%20without%20any%20strings%20attached.%20Niger%2C%20Mali%2C%20Burkina%20Faso%2C%20Chad%2C%20Equatorial%20Guinea%20and%20the%20Central%20African%20Republic%20(CAR)%2C%20all%20of%20which%20have%20seen%20coups%20d'%C3%A9tat%20in%20recent%20times%2C%20have%20sought%20and%20appreciated%20Russian%20presence%20as%20they%20push%20for%20extraction%20from%20Western%20tutelage.%20Russia%20has%20also%20added%20a%20new%20department%20to%20its%20foreign%20ministry%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20continent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20say%2C%20however%2C%20there%20are%20no%20free%20lunches%E2%80%94especially%20in%20diplomacy.%20Gold%2C%20diamond%20and%20strategic%20bases%20(Libya%2C%20Mali%20and%20Sudan)%20have%20thus%20become%20a%20currency%20the%20current%20African%20rulers%20trade%20for%20security%20and%20the%20supposed%20stability%20of%20their%20regimes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20these%20shifting%20sands%2C%20the%20French%20have%20dawdled%20away%2C%20with%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20not%20helping%20his%20case%20by%20accusing%20African%20leaders%20of%20being%20%E2%80%98ungrateful'.%20Eternity%2C%20alas%2C%20is%20not%20the%20law%20in%20international%20discourse.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20Shouldn't%20Waste%20Time%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20time%20India%20acted%20fast%20amid%20these%20changing%20equations.%20It%20is%20a%20major%20stakeholder%20in%20the%20region%20and%20has%20a%20historical%20connection%20with%20it.%20Through%20its%20exceptional%20capacity-building%20programme%20and%20infrastructural%20development%20initiatives%2C%20it%20is%20expanding%20its%20soft%20power%20projection%20and%20strategic%20engagement%20with%20the%20continent.%20The%20inclusion%20of%20the%20African%20Union%20(AU)%20in%20the%20G20%20under%20India's%20Presidency%20and%20the%20firm%20support%20for%20Africa's%20cause%20through%20the%20policy%20of%20%E2%80%98Vasudhaiva%20Kutumbakam'%20point%20to%20genuine%20intent.%20In%202018%2C%20PM%20Modi%20listed%20the%20%E2%80%98Ten%20Guiding%20Principles'%20for%20India's%20engagement%20with%20Africa.%20Under%20him%2C%20the%20Centre%20has%20also%20been%20trying%20to%20increase%20high-level%20visits%20to%20the%20region.%20It%20will%2C%20however%2C%20be%20useful%20to%20move%20quickly%20on%20holding%20the%20fourth%20round%20of%20the%20India-Africa%20Forum%20Summit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAfrica%20Treads%20Carefully%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20quite%20likely%20that%20Moscow%20and%20Beijing%20might%20align%20their%20strategies%20in%20the%20continent.%20While%20the%20latter%20may%20position%20itself%20as%20the%20key%20security%20provider%20and%20the%20largest%20seller%20of%20arms%20to%20the%20continent%2C%20China%20can%20cement%20its%20status