able%20region%20has%20long%20been%20avoided%20due%20to%20its%20extreme%20terrain%2C%20harsh%20climate%2C%20and%20lack%20of%20infrastructure.%20But%20for%20migrants%20desperate%20to%20reach%20the%20US%2C%20it%20has%20become%20an%20unavoidable%20gateway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20crossing%20the%20Darien%20Gap%20face%20steep%20mountains%2C%20muddy%20swamplands%2C%20fast-moving%20rivers%2C%20and%20dangerous%20wildlife.%20The%20jungle%20is%20home%20to%20venomous%20snakes%2C%20jaguars%2C%20and%20deadly%20insects.%20However%2C%20the%20most%20significant%20threats%20are%20from%20criminal%20organisations%20that%20control%20the%20route.%20The%20smuggling%20networks%2C%20drug%20cartels%2C%20and%20armed%20groups%20demand%20payments%2C%20rob%20migrants%2C%20or%20subject%20them%20to%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20'Donkey%20Route'%20through%20Darien%20Gap%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20Indians%20attempting%20to%20enter%20the%20US%20illegally%20follow%20what%20is%20known%20as%20the%20'donkey%20route'.%20This%20involves%20travelling%20to%20countries%20such%20as%20Central%20American%20nations%20like%20Panama%2C%20Costa%20Rica%2C%20El%20Salvador%2C%20and%20Guatemala%20where%20visas%20are%20easy%20to%20obtain.%20From%20there%2C%20they%20make%20their%20way%20to%20Mexico%20and%20then%20attempt%20to%20enter%20the%20US%2C%20often%20with%20the%20help%20of%20coyotes%20(human%20smugglers)%20who%20charge%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20for%20the%20dangerous%20crossing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20method%20has%20become%20increasingly%20popular%20as%20direct%20air%20routes%20to%20the%20US%20become%20harder%20due%20to%20stricter%20visa%20regulations.%20Smugglers%2C%20mafia%20gangs%2C%20and%20organised%20crime%20syndicates%20take%20advantage%20of%20these%20migrants%2C%20promising%20them%20safe%20passage%20but%20often%20abandoning%20them%20in%20life-threatening%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EScale%20of%20migrants%20crossing%20the%20Darien%20Gap%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20the%20number%20of%20people%20crossing%20the%20Darien%20Gap%20has%20skyrocketed.%20In%202023%2C%20over%205.2%20lakh%20migrants%20made%20the%20journey%20-%20more%20than%20double%20the%20figure%20from%20the%20previous%20year.%20By%202024%2C%20over%203%20lakh%20had%20already%20crossed%2C%20though%20the%20numbers%20had%20slightly%20declined%20due%20to%20increased%20enforcement%20efforts%2C%20Reuters%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20decade%20ago%2C%20only%20a%20few%20thousand%20people%20attempted%20this%20crossing%20annually.%20Today%2C%20it%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20high-risk%20migration%20highway%2C%20with%20people%20from%20Venezuela%2C%20Haiti%2C%20Ecuador%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20India%20making%20the%20perilous%20trek.%20The%20journey%20can%20take%20anywhere%20from%207%20to%2015%20days%2C%20with%20migrants%20facing%20food%20and%20water%20shortages%2C%20disease%2C%20and%20rampant%20crime.%20Many%20do%20not%20survive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHumanitarian%20Crisis%20in%20the%20Darien%20Gap%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Darien%20Gap%20remains%20a%20humanitarian%20disaster%2C%20with%20312%20migrant%20deaths%20or%20disappearances%20reported%20from%202015-2022%20and%20229%20more%20between%202021%20and%202023.%20In%202023%20alone%2C%20MSF%20(Medecins%20Sans%20Frontieres%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Doctors%20Without%20Borders)%20treated%20676%20sexual%20assault%20victims%2C%20with%20233%20cases%20recorded%20in%20early%202024.%20Overcrowded%20shelters%20lack%20essentials%20like%20food%2C%20water%2C%20and%20medical%20aid%2C%20leaving%20many%20migrants%20stranded.%20Social%20media%20misinformation%2C%20often%20driven%20by%20smugglers%2C%20fuels%20crossings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20more%20migrants%20using%20this%20passage%2C%20the%20impact%20on%20local%20communities%20and%20the%20environment%20has%20also%20been%20devastating.%20Indigenous%20villages%20along%20the%20route%20are%20overwhelmed%20with%20people%2C%20while%20deforestation%20and%20pollution%20are%20worsening%20in%20the%20fragile%20jungle%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20region%20is%20also%20a%20major%20hub%20for%20human%20trafficking%20and%20cartel%20activity.%20Colombia's%20Gulf%20Clan%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20drug%20cartels%2C%20controls%20smuggling%20operations.%20They%20reportedly%20earned%20%2457%20million%20from%20migrant%20crossings%20in%20just%20the%20first%2010%20months%20of%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738842360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Ftighpbk8_darien-gap-_625x300_06_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findian-migrants-deported-darien-gap-deadly-97-km-jungle-crossing-that-migrants-brave-to-reach-us-7648580%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20United%20States%20recently%20deported%20104%20Indian%20migrants%2C%20handcuffed%20and%20shackled%20for%20a%20nearly%2024-hour%20flight%20back%20to%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findian-migrants-deported-darien-gap-deadly-97-km-jungle-crossing-that-migrants-brave-to-reach-us-7648580%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22These%20airlines%20are%20using%20Apple%20AirTags%20to%20help%20reunite%20passengers%20with%20lost%20luggage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Flight%20passengers%20wait%20at%20a%20check-in%20desk%20for%20German%20airline%20Lufthansa%20at%20Munich%20International%20Airport%20in%20Munich%2C%20southern%20Germany%2C%20on%20August%2027%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a482bcbfebcc4d029df8cf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22854%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELufthansa%20is%20one%20of%20the%20first%20airlines%20to%20offer%20the%20Apple%20AirTag%20location%20feature.%3Cp%3EMichaela%20STACHE%20