uot%3BThe%20process%20of%20deportation%20(by%20the%20US)%20is%2C%20therefore%2C%20not%20new...%20it%20has%20been%20there%20for%20years.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20policy%20applicable%20to%20only%20one%20country.%20Our%20focus%20should%20be%20on%20crackdown%20on%20illegal%20migrants%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20acknowledging%20also%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20engaging%20with%20the%20US%20to%20ensure%20deportees%20are%20not%20mistreated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%C2%A0said%20US%20authorities%20had%20not%20restrained%20women%20and%20children%2C%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bneeds%20of%20deportees%2C%20related%20to%20food%20and%20other%20necessities%2C%20including%20possible%20medical%20emergencies%26quot%3B%20were%20attended%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F191htm5o_indian-migrants-us-shackledjpg_625x300_06_February_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVideo%20posted%20by%20US%20Border%20Patrol%20showing%20shackled%20deportees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar's%20brief%20opening%20remarks%20were%20followed%20by%20a%20volley%20of%20questions%20and%20criticism%20from%20the%20opposition%20benches%2C%20including%20Trinamool%20MP%20Saket%20Gokhale%20asking%20why%20the%20Indian%20government%20could%20not%20have%20sent%20a%20plane%20-%20military%20or%20civilian%20charter%20-%20to%20bring%20back%20its%20citizens%20in%20a%20more%20humane%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20the%20fifth-largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world...%20when%20countries%20like%20Colombia%2C%20which%20don't%20even%20figure%20in%20the%20top%2010%2C%20can%20send%20an%20aircraft%20and%20bring%20their%20citizens%20back%20with%20dignity%2C%20what%20stops%20our%20government%20f