inst%20Dr%20Ambedkar.%20He%20was%20not%20considered%20worthy%20of%20Bharat%20Ratna.%20Today%20Congress%20is%20forced%20to%20say%20'Jai%20Bhim'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20is%20also%20very%20adept%20at%20changing%20colours...it%20is%20clearly%20visible%20in%20this%20that%20they%20change%20their%20mask%20so%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20government%2C%20inspired%20by%20the%20mantra%20of%20'Sabka%20Sath%2C%20Sabka%20Vikas'%2C%20gave%2010%20per%20cent%20reservation%20to%20the%20poor%20of%20the%20general%20category.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20never%20honoured%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738840800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fo95aap68_pm-modi-_625x300_06_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-model-is-family-first-pm-modis-top-quotes-from-rajya-sabha-7648220%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20addressed%20the%20Parliament%20and%20responded%20to%20the%20Motion%20of%20Thanks%20on%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu's%20address.%20P%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-model-is-family-first-pm-modis-top-quotes-from-rajya-sabha-7648220%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi-Dehradun%20Expressway%20Is%20Now%20Open%3A%20Check%20Travel%20Time%20And%20More%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDelhi-Dehradun%20Expressway%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20Delhi-Dehradun%20Expressway%20has%20reached%20a%20new%20milestone%20by%20opening%20a%203.5%20km%20section.%20This%20is%20part%20of%20a%20larger%2031.6%20km%20project%20designed%20to%20shorten%20travel%20times%20between%20the%20two%20cities%20significantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Road%20Transpo