itness%20during%20the%20experiment%2C%20rather%20than%20lose%20fat%20or%20build%20muscle%2C%20sports%20scientists%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Loughborough%2C%20UK%2C%20monitored%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Hugo%2C%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-fat-keto-diet-should-be-avoided-cardiologist-says-2020-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh-fat%3C%2Fa%3E%20diet%2C%20gained%20more%20muscle%20than%20his%20brother%2C%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he%20performed%20worse%20and%20felt%20more%20fatigued%20during%20intense%20exercise.%20Ross%2C%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feat-more-carbs-lose-fat-build-muscle-nutritionist-advice-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh-carb%3C%2Fa%3E%20diet%2C%20didn't%20put%20on%20as%20much%20muscle%20but%20lost%20a%20little%20more%20fat%20and%20performed%20better%20in%20cardiovascular%20tests.%20The%20twins%20now%20plan%20to%20tweak%20what%20they%20eat%20depending%20on%20what%20expediton%20they're%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20experiment%20was%20anecdotal%20and%20not%20large%20enough%20to%20prove%20which%20diet%20is%20%26quot%3Bbetter.%26quot%3B%20But%20a%20sports%20physiologist%20who%20worked%20with%20the%20brothers%20told%20BI%20it%20was%20interesting%20that%20both%20got%20fitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c2214380-36f9-4922-af83-d79e90751d53%5C%22%3EThe%20twins%20added%20500%20calories%20of%20carbs%20or%20fat%20to%20their%20diets%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223961%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Turner%20Twins%20standing%20in%20a%20warehouse%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a348e5bfebcc4d029dcd07%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222646%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Turners%20took%20detailed%20tests%20before%20starting%20the%20experiment.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20Turners%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20experiment%2C%20both%20Hugo%20and%20Ross%20balanced%20carbs%20and%20fats%20in%20their%20diets.%20For%20the%20experiment%2C%20they%20ate%20around%203%2C500%20calories%20each%20day%2C%202%2C500%20from%20three%20meals%20and%20two%20snacks%20from%20a%20food%20delivery%20service%20called%20Frive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20didn't%20want%20to%20go%20to%20extremes%20so%20made%20their%20diets%20nutritionally%20different%20by%20only%20500%20calories%20per%20day%3A%20Hugo%20from%20fats%2C%20and%20Ross%20from%20carbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHugo%20(on%20the%20high-fat%20diet)%20followed%20Frive's%20low-carb%20meal%20plan%20and%20added%20high-fat%20foods%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsimple-longevity-tricks-to-improve-diet-routine-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eolive%20oil%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20butter%2C%20nuts%2C%20eggs%2C%20and%20avocado.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Ross%20followed%20a%20%26quot%3Bbalanced%26quot%3B%20meal%20plan%20and%20added%20calories%20from%20high-carb%20foods%20such%20as%20pasta%20and%20rice%2C%20while%20avoiding%20high-fat%20foods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20support%20their%20training%2C%20they%20also%20consumed%20350-calorie%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinding-best-way-add-protein-to-coffee-taste-test%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprotein%20shakes%3C%2Fa%3E%20each%20day.%20Keeping%20your%20protein%20intake%20high%20is%20important%20for%20muscle%20building%20and%20repair%2C%20so%20was%20a%20non-negotiable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Turners%20did%20similar%20workouts%20featuring%20a%20mixture%20of%20cardio%20and%20strength%20training%2C%20using%20home%20gym%20equipment%2C%20and%20rested%20every%20three%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20weren't%20perfect%20with%20our%20training%20but%20we%20weren't%20perfect%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Ross%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b14e228d-b54a-406b-b8ce-a0b54bbc88f0%5C%22%3EThe%20low-carb%20and%20low-fat%20diets%20felt%20restrictive%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224240%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hugo%20Turner%20holding%20a%20block%20of%20cheese%20and%20Ross%20Turner%20holding%20raw%20spaghetti.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a349647bb3f854015bc693%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222832%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHugo%20followed%20a%20high-fat%20diet%2C%20whereas%20Ross%20followed%20a%20high-carb%20diet.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20Turners%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHugo%20said%20he%20found%20the%20high-fat%20diet%20%26quot%3Bincredibly%20difficult%26quot%3B%20mentally%20and%20didn't%20feel%20energized%20or%20motivated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20never%20felt%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20eating%20at%20least%20six%20times%20a%20day%20and%20never%20felt%20full%20or%20satisfied%2C%20hence%20I%20was%20constantly%20hungry.%20But%20equally%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20the%20crashes%20that%20I%20would%20probably%20associate%20with%20a%20higher-carb%20diet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHugo%20said%20the%20high-fat%20diet%20felt%20relatively%20repetitive%20and%20he%20missed%20feeling%20full.%20Fat%20contains%20nine%20calories%20per%20gram%20whereas%20carbs%20(and%20protein)%20contain%20four.%20So%20you%20can%20eat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-volume-high-fiber-foods-lose-fat-keep-muscle-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20carbs%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20calories%20as%20a%20smaller%20portion%20of%20high-fat%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20reason%2C%20some%20people%20don't%20feel%20so%20full%20on%20a%20high-fat%2C%20low-carb%20diet.%20However%2C%20others%20find%20they%20don't%20feel%20satiated%20without%20consuming%20a%20decent%20amount%20of%20fat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoss%20said%20he%20missed%20the%20mouthfeel%20of%20high-fat%20foods%2C%20but%20felt%20full.%20He%20would%20occasionally%20have%20a%20small%20piece%20of%20dark%20chocolate%2C%20which%20helped%20with%20the%20cravings%20a%20little.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20my%20first%20piece%20of%20cheese%20in%2012%20weeks%20yesterday%2C%20and%20it%20tasted%20insanely%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20Ross%20said%20after%20the%20experiment%2C%20and%20they%20agreed%20were%20really%20looking%20forward%20to%20eating%20pizza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22433735f6-faa0-4f1d-9b10-a5869b7da30e%5C%22%3EEndurance%20exercises%20were%20tougher%20on%20the%20high-fat%20diet%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Turners%20bench%20pressing%20and%20running%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a34a20eb4be2fff9a388c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Turners%20tested%20their%20bench%20press%20abilities%20and%20VO2%20max%20on%20their%20respective%20diets.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20Turners%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20and%20after%20the%20experiment%2C%20the%20Turners%20measured%20their%20body%20composition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20the%20high-fat%20diet%2C%20Hugo%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGained%201%20kilogram%20(6.6%20pounds)%20of%20muscle%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELost%200.3%20kilograms%20(0.6%20pounds)%20of%20fat%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGained%20internal%20(visceral)%20fat%3A%20increasing%20from%2011.4%25%20to%2012.6%25%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESaw%20no%20change%20to%20his%20cholesterol%20levels%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20the%20high-carb%20diet%2C%20Ross%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGained%201%20kilogram%20(2.2%20pounds)%20of%20muscle%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELost%200.9%20kilograms%20(two%20pounds)%20of%20fat.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELost%20internal%20(visceral)%20fat%3A%20decreasing%20from%2011.5%25%20to%2011.1%25%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-lower-cholesterol%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELowered%20his%20cholesterol%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Turners%20also%20tested%20their%20strength%20and%20fitness%2C%20including%20documenting%20changes%20in%20their%20bench%20presses%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvo2-max-explained-what-is-good-how-improve-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVO2%20max%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20back%20squats%2C%20among%20other%20exercises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20both%20got%20better%20results%20on%20the%20strength%20tests%20by%20almost%20the%20exact%20same%20amount%2C%20but%20Hugo%20(high-fat)%20lacked%20energy%20in%20the%20cardiovascular%20fitness%20and%20endurance%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAround%2040%20minutes%20into%20the%20running%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20completely%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20felt%20dreadful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20collected%20by%20the%20researchers%20backed%20up%20Hugo's%20feelings%3A%20By%20testing%20their%20lactate%20thresholds%20while%20running%20(which%20involved%20taking%20blood%20pricks%20from%20their%20ear%20lobes%20every%2010%20minutes)%2C%20they%20could%20see%20Hugo%20was%20struggling.%20Blood%20lactate%20correlates%20with%20how%20hard%20someone%20is%20working%20metabolically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoss%2C%20who%20was%20able%20to%20run%20for%20longer%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20experiment%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BCarbs%20are%20very%20good%20and%20readily%20available%20for%20providing%20the%20body%20with%20energy%20at%20higher%20intensities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2262f8d655-8055-4939-9912-3dd390c755e7%5C%22%3EThere's%20no%20such%20thing%20as%20the%20'best%20diet'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222832%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hugo%20Turner%20with%20his%20head%20in%20his%20hands%20and%20Ross%20Turner%20celebrating.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a34aaf7bb3f854015bc6ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222124%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERoss%2C%20on%20the%20high-carb%20diet%2C%20performed%20better%20in%20the%20fitness%20tests.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20Turners%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESteven%20Harris%2C%20a%20performance%20physiologist%20at%20Loughborough%20University%20who%20worked%20with%20the%20Turners%2C%20said%20it's%20notable%20that%20both%20twins%20saw%20improvements%20in%20cardiovascular%20fitness%20and%20metabolic%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20high-carb%20diet%20appeared%20to%20help%20Ross%20to%20push%20himself%20slightly%20harder%2C%20possibly%20during%20his%2012%20weeks%20of%20training%20and%20not%20just%20the%20final%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20detailed%20breakdowns%20can%20be%20helpful%20for%20elite%20athletes%2C%20Harris%20advises%20the%20average%20person%20to%20eat%20a%20balance%20of%20carbs%20and%20fats%20that%20makes%20them%20feel%20their%20best%20and%20fuels%20their%20lifestyle%2C%20rather%20than%20copying%20what%20others%20say%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bbest%26quot%3B%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGenerally%2C%20if%20you%20know%20you're%20going%20to%20do%20a%20tough%20training%20session%2C%20you'll%20likely%20perform%20better%20if%20you've%20got%20some%20carbs%20in%20the%20tank%2C%20Harris%20said%2C%20which%20aligns%20with%20what%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-low-carb-diet-bad-high-intensity-exercise-muscle-loss-2021-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enutrition%20and%20sports%20experts%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20previously%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Turners%20both%20prefer%20eating%20diets%20with%20a%20balance%20of%20protein%2C%20carbs%2C%20and%20fat%20day-to-day%2C%20they%20said%20they%20might%20tweak%20their%20diets%20before%20particular%20expeditions%20going%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20ahead%20of%20high-intensity%20activities%20that%20raise%20the%20heart%20rate%20a%20lot%2C%20like%20cycling%2C%20running%2C%20or%20kite%20skiing%2C%20they%20would%20up%20their%20carbohydrates%20beforehand.%20Conversely%2C%20if%20they%20were%20doing%20a%20walking%20expedition%20or%20something%20slower-paced%2C%20they%20would%20choose%20a%20higher-fat%20diet%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffat-loss-diet-high-carb-energy-twin-experiment-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738839175000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a34aff7bb3f854015bc6b3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffat-loss-diet-high-carb-energy-twin-experiment-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20twin%20followed%20a%20high-fat%20diet%20while%20the%20other%20ate%20high-carb.%20Their%20experiment%20will%20change%20what%20they%20eat%20before%20different%20activities%2C%20from%20cycling%20to%20a%20long%20walk.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rhosie%40businessinsider.com%20(Rachel%20Hosie)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffat-loss-diet-high-carb-energy-twin-experiment-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Flurry%20of%20international%20naval%20drills%20around%20Philippines%20prompts%20complaints%20from%20Beijing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738838785000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117981686%2Cimgsize-488007.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fflurry-of-international-naval-drills-around-philippines-prompts-complaints-from-beijing%2Farticleshow%2F117981240.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F117981240.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERecent%20naval%20drills%20in%20the%20Philippines%20involving%20the%20US%2C%20Japan%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20the%20Philippines%20have%20drawn%20criticism%20from%20China%2C%20which%20claims%20the