of%20equity%20research%20for%20Canada%20and%20the%20UK%2C%20during%20a%20February%205%20webinar%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20almost%20impossible%20for%20American%20and%20Canadian%20companies%20to%20plan%20and%20issue%20guidance%20to%20investors%20when%20they%20don't%20know%20what%20next%20month%20holds%20%E2%80%94%20much%20less%20next%20quarter%20or%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20top%20minds%20at%20BMO%20seem%20confident%20that%20Trump's%20tariff%20talk%20will%20be%20more%20bark%20than%20bite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20long%20said%20that%20opportunities%20come%20about%20when%20people%20%E2%80%94%20investors%20and%20markets%20%E2%80%94%20overreact%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Brian%20Belski%2C%20the%20firm's%20chief%20investment%20strategist%2C%20on%20the%20webinar.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20we%20believe%20that%20there%20was%20a%20clear%20overreaction%20to%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fa94ee30-51b0-4793-a20a-a4aadcae7d58%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EStay%20calm%2C%20and%20play%20it%20safe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBMO's%20message%20to%20clients%20right%20now%20is%20best%20summed%20up%20by%20a%20four-word%20statement%20from%20Belski%3A%20%26quot%3BRemain%20calm%20and%20disciplined.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20neither%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20nor%20the%20Canadian%20S%26amp%3BP%2FTSX%20Composite%20Index%20have%20gone%20far%20lately%2C%20both%20indexes%20have%20had%20dizzying%20intra-day%20swings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%20volatility%2C%20BMO%20is%20sticking%20with%20year-end%20targets%20that%20imply%20double-digit%20gains%20since%20it%20believes%20both%20US%20and%20Canadian%20markets%20are%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-invest-2025-stock-market-outlook-investing-strategy-bmo-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elong-term%20uptrends%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Belski%20said%20he's%20thought%20US%20stocks%20were%20set%20for%2025%20strong%20years%20since%20arriving%20at%20BMO%20in%202012%2C%20and%20he's%20not%20changing%20now.%20He%20added%20that%20Canadian%20stocks%20are%20%26quot%3Bcoming%20along%20for%20the%20ride.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithin%20secular%20bulls%2C%20you%20can%20have%20cyclical%20bears%2C%20which%20we%20clearly%20did%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%202018%2C%26quot%3B%20Belski%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20a%20clear%20bear%20market%20during%20Covid%2C%20and%20another%20bear%20market%20in%202022.%20So%20you%20can%20have%20these%20opportunities%2C%20from%20a%20fundamental%20perspective%2C%20to%20be%20involved.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20that%20said%2C%20the%20top%20strategist%20said%20investors%20should%20take%20a%20granular%20look%20at%20individual%20stocks%2C%20instead%20of%20simply%20buying%20shares%20of%20US-based%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWorry%20more%20about%20the%20implicit%2C%20bottoms-up%20view%20on%20the%20stocks%2C%20versus%20trying%20to%20make%20the%20big%20market%20call%2C%26quot%3B%20Belski%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20stock-pickers%20shouldn't%20get%20greedy%20or%20caught%20up%20in%20the%20hype%20of%20a%20promising%20company%20or%20market-shifting%20trend.%20Nor%20should%20they%20make%20huge%20bets%20based%20on%20policy%20views%20or%20predictions%2C%20especially%20in%20this%20highly%20uncertain%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20is%20not%20the%20time%20to%20be%20hitting%20home%20runs%2C%26quot%3B%20Belski%20said.%20%26quot%3BNow%20it's%20time%20to%20be%20hitting%20singles%20and%20doubles%2C%20and%20it's%20time%20to%20be%20more%20fundamental.%20It's%20time%20to%20turn%20off%20the%20rhetoric.%20It's%20time%20to%20kind%20of%20take%20two%20steps%20back%20and%20look%20at%20the%20mosaic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20should%20zero%20in%20on%20four%20key%20aspects%20of%20companies%2C%20Belski%20said%3A%20their%20valuation%2C%20growth%2C%20operating%20performance%2C%20and%20price%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20that%20lens%2C%20Belski's%20view%20is%20that%20US%20stocks%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-economy-how-to-invest-strategy-valuations-ai-page-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erichly%20valued%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20have%20little%20room%20for%20error%2C%20though%20they%20can%20justify%20that%20premium%20due%20to%20their%20remarkably%20consistent%20earnings%20growth%2C%20plus%20top-tier%20marks%20in%20free%20cash%20flow%2C%20return%20on%20invested%20capital%2C%20and%20debt%20to%20equity.%20Canadian%20stocks%20don't%20get%20nearly%20as%20much%20attention%20as%20their%20US%20peers%2C%20though%20they%20score%20well%20there%20also.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20equity%20markets%20in%20Canada%20and%20the%20United%20States%20%E2%80%94%20relative%20to%20other%20developed%20markets%20in%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20are%20on%20much%20better%20footing%2C%26quot%3B%20Belski%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20that%20said%2C%20certain%20sectors%20look%20like%20better%20bets%20than%20others.%20BMO%20is%20especially%20bullish%20about%20four%20investment%20ideas%2C%20which%20Belski%20reiterated%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcapitalmarkets.bmo.com%2Fen%2Fnews-insights%2Fresearch-strategy%2Fmitigate-the-chaos-with-calm-process-and-discipline%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecent%20note%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%3Cstrong%3Econsumer%20discretionary%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%3Cstrong%3Efinancials%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%3Cstrong%3Ereal%20estate%20investment%20trusts%20(REITs)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cstrong%3Etechnology%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsumer%20discretionary%20and%20technology%20look%20like%20solid%20bets%20in%20a%20continued%20economic%20expansion%2C%20and%20the%20latter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-valuation-how-to-invest-investing-strategy-bmo-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20historically%20done%20best%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20up%20markets%2C%20BMO%20has%20sa