2C%20have%20ridden%20the%20ebbs%20and%20flows%20of%20public%20markets.%20A%20typical%20family%20office's%20performance%20has%20matched%20or%20trailed%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%2C%20being%20generally%20down%20by%2010%25%20to%2015%25%20in%202022%2C%20slightly%20recovering%20with%20an%208%25%20to%2012%25%20return%20in%202023%2C%20and%20finally%20seeing%20good%20gains%20in%202024%2C%20with%20the%20typical%20European%20family%20office%20up%20about%2013%25%20to%2015%25%20and%20US%20family%20office%20up%20by%20about%2015%25%20to%2017%25%2C%20Husain%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20generally%20because%20of%20their%20heavy%20exposure%20to%20the%20broad%20US%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20the%20client%20is%20in%20the%20US%20or%20Asia%2C%2080%20to%2090%25%20of%20their%20book%20wealth%20is%20in%20US%20public%20equities%20or%20US%20private%20markets%2C%20Husain%20noted.%20It%20sounds%20concentrated%2C%20but%20many%20started%20with%20less%20exposure%2C%20near%2040%25%20to%2050%25%20and%20over%20the%20past%20decade%20or%20so%2C%20US%20outperformance%20has%20increased%20that%20exposure%20heavily.%20It's%20why%20everything%20from%20US%20inflation%20to%20Washington's%20policies%20concerns%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20surprised%2C%26quot%3B%20Husain%20said%20of%20the%20number%20of%20clients%2C%20some%20of%20which%20have%20upward%20of%20%2430%20to%20%2450%20billion%20in%20wealth%20that%20have%2C%20say%2C%20%2412%20billion%20just%20sitting%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fs%26amp%3Bp_500%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20has%20the%20index%20giant's%20performance%20been%20stellar%2C%20especially%20over%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20racking%20in%20gains%20above%2020%25%2C%20but%20US%20markets%20are%20transparent%2C%20built%20on%20a%20strong%20and%20stable%20currency%2C%20with%20leading%20companies%20run%20by%20high-performing%20CEOs%20with%20the%20best%20pay%20packages%20who%20find%20ways%20to%20squeeze%20margin%2C%20he%20said.%20All%20of%20that%20has%20been%20a%20strong%20attractor%20for%20wealth%20from%20every%20corner%20of%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trend%20toward%20indexing%20and%20away%20from%20active%20investing%20isn't%20new%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20as%20expected%20for%20family%20offices%20that%20lean%20into%20customized%20investing%20strategies.%20However%2C%20ultra-high-net-worth%20individuals%20have%20been%20firing%20their%20active%20managers%20because%20it's%20just%20been%20hard%20to%20beat%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20now%2C%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%202025%2C%20they're%20finding%20themselves%20super%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-global-currencies-are-reshuffling-amid-tariff-threats-fx-rates-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elong%20the%20US%20dollar%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20US%20assets%2C%20and%20for%20risk%20purposes%2C%20there's%20a%20strong%20sense%20that%20they%20should%20be%20diversified.%20But%20clients%20had%20the%20same%20concern%20in%202022%20and%202023%2C%20leading%20them%20to%20diversify%20in%20foreign%20markets%20like%20China%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20Europe%2C%20which%20didn't%20really%20work%20out%20either%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20into%202025%2C%20questions%20about%20the%20big%20risks%20and%20opportunities%20in%20US%20equities%20have%20dominated%20the%20conversation%20across%20offices%20as%20they%20seek%20ways%20to%20balance%20exposure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20clients%20are%20like%2C%20'Look%2C%20we%20are%20limited.%20We're%20a%20family%20office%2C%20we%20don't%20have%20thousands%20of%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Husain%20said.%20So%20they%20either%20throw%20their%20human%20resources%20toward%20private%20markets%20or%2C%20if%20they%20decide%20to%20have%20active%20managers%2C%20they%20become%20very%20selective%2C%20seeking%20contrarian%20managers%20who%20oversee%20the%20Japanese%20and%20European%20markets%20or%20who%20can%20find%20alpha%E2%80%94above%20market%20returns%E2%80%94%20in%20US%20small%20caps%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20small-cap%20market%20is%20full%20of%20stocks%20that%20can%20outperform.%20But%20not%20if%20you%20go%20into%20it%20passively%20through%20the%20Russell%202000%2C%20which%20is%20poorly%20made%2C%20merging%20thousands%20of%20low-quality%20companies%20with%20weak%20earnings%20and%20balance%20sheets%2C%20Husain%20said.%20In%20this%20instance%2C%20family%20offices%20are%20willing%20to%20hire%20a%20small%20manager%20with%20%24500%20million%20to%20%243%20billion%20of%20AUM%2C%20who%20can%20be%20very%20selective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EObviously%2C%20these%20companies%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20more%20volatile%2C%20but%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariff-plan-external-revenue-service-imports-impact-consumers-economy-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebullish%20view%3C%2Fa%3E%20family%20offices%20have%20on%20US%20growth%20under%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20suggests%20that%20small%20local%20companies%20may%20do%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20you%20start%20going%20off%20index%2C%20and%20you're%20owning%20companies%20that%20are%20not%20going%20to%20get%20the%20momentum%20flow%20of%20just%20passive%20money%2C%20everything%20comes%20down%20to%20really%20deep%20fundamental%20analysis%2C%26quot%3B%20Husain%20said.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20things%20like%20a%20firm's%20three-year%20business%20plan%2C%20execution%20success%2C%20and%20inflection%20points%20really%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20developed%20markets%2C%20valuations%20are%20just%20too%20attractive.%20Even%20as%20European%20growth%20stalls%2C%20Husain%20says%20some%20of%20the%20hottest%20stocks%20can%20be%20found%20there.%20Names%20like%20Rheinmetall%2C%20a%20German%20manufacturer%20of%20weapons%2C%20ammunition%2C%20and%20armored%20vehicles%2C%20up%20about%20124%25%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20or%20Italian%20radar%20and%20aerospace%20defense%20maker%20Leonardo%2C%20up%2078%25%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20have%20outperformed%20or%20done%20just%20as%20well%20as%20Nvidia%20over%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20German%20Dax%20Performance%20index%20(DAX)%2C%20which%20includes%2040%20major%20German%20blue-chip%20companies%2C%20is%20already%20outperforming%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500.%20It%20is%20up%20almost%208%25%20this%20year%20compared%20to%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%203%25.%20It%20was%20up%20almost%2028%25%20over%20the%20last%2012%20months%20compared%20to%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%2022%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20there%20are%20definite%20pockets%20of%20outperformance.%20Husain%20said%20family%20offices%20will%20look%20for%20an%20active%20manager%20in%20those%20strong%20foreign%20markets%20to%20find%20winning%20bets%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20face%20of%20trade%20wars%2C%20which%20can%20create%20opportunistic%20momentum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-wealthiest-investing-in-the-stock-market-2025-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738837802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a80acbaab37011780b81bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-wealthiest-investing-in-the-stock-market-2025-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20idea%20that%20ultra-high-net-worth%20individuals%20are%20more%20concerned%20with%20wealth%20preservation%20than%20alpha%20generation%20isn't%20necessarily%20true.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lmaidan%40businessinsider.com%20(Laila%20Maidan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-wealthiest-investing-in-the-stock-market-2025-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China's%20economy%20gets%20New%20Year%20boost%20from%20holiday%20travel%20and%