htmare-7646326%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereportedly%20shackled%20and%20handcuffed%3C%2Fa%3E%20aboard%20a%20US%20military%20aircraft%20before%20landing%20in%20Amritsar%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20has%20defended%20its%20position%2C%20citing%20international%20obligations%2C%20but%20Opposition%20leaders%20have%20accused%20it%20of%20inaction%20and%20failing%20to%20protect%20Indian%20citizens%20from%20alleged%20mistreatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Saket%20Gokhale%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party's%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20speaking%20shortly%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-new-on-for-several-years-s-jaishankar-after-us-deports-104-indian-migrants-7647172%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EExternal%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%3C%2Fa%3E's%20speech%20in%20Parliament%20today%2C%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20had%20previously%20arranged%20special%20flights%20to%20evacuate%20its%20citizens%20from%20crisis%20zones.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbudget-session-day-6-live-updates-congress-to-raise-inhuman-deportation-of-indians-from-us-7645639%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFollow%20Parliament%20Budget%20Session%20LIVE%20UPDATES%20here%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20the%20fifth%20largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world%20and%20soon%20we%20will%20become%20'Vishwa%20Guru'.%20As%20'Vishwa%20Guru'%2C%20our%20citizens%20are%20being%20shackled%20in%20chains%20when%20countries%20like%20Colombia%2C%20which%20doesn't%20even%20figure%20in%20the%20top%2010%2C%20can%20send%20an%20aircraft%20and%20bring%20their%20citizens%20back%20with%20dignity.%20What%20stops%20our%20government%20from%20sending%20an%20aircraft%3F%20We%20don't%20have%20a%20shortage%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Gokhale%20in%20Parliament.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20early%20months%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20India%20mounted%20large-scale%20evacuations%20from%20several%20countries.%20In%202020%2C%20Air%20India%20operated%20special%20flights%20to%20bring%20back%20Indians%20from%20Wuhan%2C%20China%20-%20the%20epicentre%20of%20the%20outbreak.%20Similarly%2C%20India%20had%20conducted%20mass%20evacuations%20from%20Ukraine%20when%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20broke%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20this%20precedent%2C%20Opposition%20leaders%20have%20questioned%20why%20the%20Indian%20government%20did%20not%20take%20similar%20steps%20to%20bring%20back%20deported%20Indian%20nationals%20from%20the%20US%2C%20instead%20of%20allowing%20them%20to%20be%20transported%20under%20American%20authorities'%20strict%20security%20protocols.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20did%20the%20US%20military%20plane%20land%20on%20Indian%20soil%3F%20Why%20were%20our%20citizens%20brought%20in%20handcuffs%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20asked%20in%20Parliament.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20baffles%20me%20is%20that%20the%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20seems%20focussed%20on%20defending%20the%20US%20deportation%20policies%20rather%20than%20the%20interest%20of%20our%20citizens%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Gokhale.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%2C%20speaking%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20defended%20the%20government's%20stance%2C%20arguing%20that%20every%20country%20has%20an%20obligation%20to%20take%20back%20its%20nationals%20if%20they%20are%20found%20to%20be%20living%20illegally%20abroad.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20the%20deportations%20were%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20US%20Immigration%20and%20Customs%20Enforcement%20(ICE)%20under%20standard%20procedures%20in%20place%20since%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20deportation%20by%20the%20US%20is%20organised%20and%20executed%20by%20ICE%20authorities.%20Their%20standard%20operating%20procedure%20provides%20for%20the%20use%20of%20restraints%2C%20but%20we%20have%20been%20informed%20that%20women%20and%20children%20are%20not%20restrained%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20government%20was%20engaging%20with%20US%20authorities%20to%20ensure%20that%20deportees%20were%20not%20mistreated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20in%20our%20collective%20interest%20to%20encourage%20legal%20mobility%20and%20discourage%20illegal%20movement%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Embassy%20in%20India%20has%20stated%20that%20while%20it%20cannot%20share%20specific%20details%2C%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bvigorously%20enforcing%26quot%3B%20border%20and%20immigration%20laws%20and%20that%20these%20actions%20send%20a%20%26quot%3Bclear%20message%3A%20illegal%20migration%20is%20not%20worth%20the%20risk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20backlash%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-considering-new-law-for-migrants-safety-amid-us-deportation-row-7646407%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECentre%20is%20considering%20enacting%20a%20new%20law%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20tentatively%20titled%20the%20Overseas%20Mobility%20(Facilitation%20and%20Welfare)%20Bill%2C%202024.%20The%20legislation%20aims%20to%20promote%20%26quot%3Bsafe%2C%20orderly%2C%20and%20regular%20migration%20for%20overseas%20employment%26quot%3B%20and%20could%20serve%20as%20a%20framework%20for%20future%20deportation%20and%20immigration%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738837560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fljnqbffo_jaishankar-saket-gokhale-_625x300_06_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-migrants-deported-s-jaishankar-why-isnt-india-sending-planes-opposition-vs-centre-over-deportation-row-7647569%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20a%20massive%20political%20row%20over%20the%20deportation%20of%20over%20100%20Indian%20nationals%20from%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20Oppo