ofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-japan-summit-what-to-expect%2Famp_articleshow%2F117979520.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-japan-summit-what-to-expect%2Famp_articleshow%2F117979520.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Is%20Deported%20From%20US%2C%20Who%20Isn't%3A%20An%20NDTV%20Explainer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20axe%20of%20deportation%20hangs%20on%20about%201.4%20million%20illegal%20immigrants%20who%20once%20had%20the%20American%20dream.%20With%20the%20Donald%20Trump%20administration's%20crackdown%20on%20the%20borders%20and%20his%20vow%20to%20send%20back%20anyone%20who%20had%20entered%20the%20US%20illegally%2C%20the%20message%20is%20clear%3A%20the%20dream%20was%20a%20nightmare%20in%20waiting%3B%20that%20they%20would%20be%20sent%20back%20chained%20in%20planes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20illegal%20route%20to%20the%20US%20involves%20unseen%20dangers%2C%20one%20could%20only%20get%20a%20glimpse%20on%20the%20adventure%20shows%20and%20documentaries.%20Illegally%20entering%20another%20country%20involves%20paying%20lakhs%20to%20human%20traffickers%20and%20%26quot%3Bprotection%20money%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20drug%20mafia.%20Many%20are%20raped%20and%20those%20unable%20to%20pay%20are%20killed.%20The%20next%20hurdles%20are%20the%20dense%20and%20inhospitable%20forests%20and%20diseases%20that%20do%20not%20spare%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnown%20as%20the%20'donkey'%20route%20in%20the%20Indian%20subcontinent%2C%20this%20isn't%20an%20easy%20way.%20Neither%20does%20it%20guarantee%20an%20American%20dream%2C%20but%20the%20trauma%20of%20a%20lifetime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-new-on-for-several-years-s-jaishankar-after-us-deports-104-indian-migrants-7647172%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BProcess%20Of%20Deportation%20Not%20New%26quot%3B%3A%20S%20Jaishankar%20On%20US%20Sending%20Back%20104%20Indians%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20all%20the%20immigrants%20manage%20to%20reach%20the%20country%20of%20their%20choice%2C%20mostly%20the%20UK%20back%20in%20the%201980s%20and%20the%20US%20over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20they%20must%20convince%20an%20immigration%20judge%20why%20they%20shouldn't%20be%20sent%20back.%20This%20is%20tricky%20and%20many%20claim%20a%20threat%20to%20life%20back%20home%20to%20seek%20refugee%20on%20humanitarian%20grounds.%20This%20doesn't%20have%20a%20100%25%20success%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Is%20Deported%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Immigration%20and%20Customs%20Enforcement%20(ICE)%20is%20the%20custodian%20of%20the%20deportation%20process.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usa.gov%2Fdeportation-process%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20ICE%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20US%20may%20detain%20and%20deport%20non-citizens%20who%20violate%20their%20visas%2C%20participate%20in%20criminal%20acts%2C%20and%20are%20a%20threat%20to%20public%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20immigrants%20who%20cross%20the%20border%20illegally%20or%20are%20trafficked%20by%20agents%20without%20valid%20documents%20are%20first%20detained%20and%20taken%20to%20a%20detention%20centre.%20They%20stay%20there%20until%20they%20are%20produced%20before%20the%20immigration%20court%2C%20which%20is%20under%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice.%20The%20court%20then%20reviews%20if%20the%20immigrant%20wants%20asylum%20and%20based%20on%20the%20circumstance%2C%20it%20orders%20removal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpolicy-to-execute-immigration-laws-us-embassy-on-deportation-of-indians-7647782%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BPolicy%20To%20Execute%20Immigration%20Laws%26quot%3B%3A%20US%20Embassy%20On%20Deportation%20Of%20Indians%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20their%20deportation%2C%20they%20can%20also%20opt%20for%20voluntary%20departure%20at%20their%20own%20expense.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20expedited%20removal%20of%20some%20non-citizens%20is%20also%20done%20without%20a%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20removal%20order%2C%20the%20US%20government%20sends%20the%20migrants%20back%20-%20by%20air%20in%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20cases.%20In%20earlier%20cases%2C%20the%20US%20has%20used%20chartered%20planes%20to%20deport%20the%20migrants%20while%20the%20latest%20are%20being%20done%20by%20military%20transport%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Is%20Not%20Deported%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20immigrants%20may%20apply%20for%20asylum%20and%20are%20allowed%20to%20remain%20in%20the%20US%20if%20they%20manage%20to%20convince%20the%20judge%20they%20face%20risk%20to%20life%20if%20they%20return%20home.%20However%2C%20very%20few%20asylum%20cases%20are%20entertained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20may%20secure%20a%20Temporary%20Protected%20Status%20(TPS)%20when%20it's%20unsafe%20for%20them%20to%20return.%20However%2C%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20countries%20are%20designated%20for%20the%20TPS.%20As%20of%20March%2031%2C%202024%2C%20around%20863%2C880%20have%20been%20living%20with%20the%20TPS%20in%20the%20US%2C%20according%20to%20the%20American%20Immigration%20Council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeferred%20Action%20for%20Childhood%20Arrivals%20(DACA)%20helps%20in%20delaying%20the%20deportation%20of%20some%20immigrants%20who%20had%20entered%20the%20US%20illegally%20with%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-migrants-deported-handcuffed-chained-thrown-like-boxes-indian-migrants-american-nightmare-7646326%5C%22%3EHandcuffed%2C%20Chained%2C%20Thrown%20Like%20Boxes%3A%20Indian%20Migrants'%20American%20Nightmare%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICE%20may%20also%20release%20some%20immigrants%20who%20are%20not%20in%20mandatory%20detention%20if%20they%20believe%20they%20are%20not%20deemed%20to%20be%20a%20risk%20in%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%201.44%20million%20immigrants%20are%20on%20the%20ICE's%20%26quot%3Bnon-detained%20docket%20with%20final%20orders%20of%20removal%26quot%3B%2C%20according%20to%20an%20official%20document%20accessed%20by%20Fox%20News.%20Nearly%2018%2C000%20of%20them%20are%20Indians%20and%20another%2038%2C000%20are%20from%20China.%20A%20big%20chunk%20-%20over%20200%2C000%20each%20-%20are%20from%20the%20Central%20and%20Latin%20American%20countries%20like%20Honduras%2C%20Guatemala%2C%20El%20Salvador%2C%20and%20Mexico.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20On%20Deportations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20FAQ%20section%20on%20its%20website%2C%20India's%20External%20Affairs%20Ministry%20says%20that%20deportations%20are%20done%20when%20a%20foreigner%20violates%20immigration%20laws%20in%20another%20country.%20In%20most%20cases%2C%20it%20says%2C%20the%20Indian%20consulate%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20intervene%20to%20prevent%20such%20deportations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20in%20cases%20where%20the%20Indian%20national%20concerned%20may%20not%20be%20at%20fault%20or%20feels%20he%20is%20being%20unfairly%20deported%2C%20this%20can%20be%20brought%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20or%20Consulate%2C%20so%20that%20it%20can%20be%20taken%20up%20with%20the%20local%20immigration%20authorities%20concerned%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECriticism%20and%20Response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20US%20military%20jet%20on%20Wednesday%20returned%20104%20Indian%20immigrants%20who%20had%20entered%20the%20US%20illegally.%20A%20video%20shared%20by%20a%20US%20border%20official%20showed%20the%20Indians%20with%20handcuffs%20and%20their%20legs%20chained%20being%20packed%20off%20into%20the%20plane.%20This%20led%20to%20an%20uproar%20in%20the%20parliament%20on%20Thursday%20with%20the%20opposition%20criticising%20as%20inhumane%20the%20way%20the%20Indian%20immigrants%20were%20chained%20and%20returned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%