are%20is%20sold%20to%20government%20clients%2C%20who%20use%20it%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20fighting%20crime%20and%20protecting%20national%20security.%20WhatsApp%20confirmed%20that%20the%20affected%20users'%20devices%20may%20have%20been%20compromised.%20The%20WhatsApp%20official%20told%20%3Cem%3EReuters%3C%2Fem%3E%20it%20had%20detected%20an%20effort%20to%20hack%20approximately%2090%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EZero-click%20hack%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat's%20concerning%20is%20that%20Paragon's%20spyware%20uses%20a%20%26quot%3Bzero-click%26quot%3B%20hack%2C%20meaning%20that%20the%20victims%20didn't%20have%20to%20click%20on%20any%20malicious%20links%20to%20be%20infected.%20Experts%20explained%20that%20a%20zero-click%20attack%20allows%20hackers%20to%20access%20a%20target's%20device%20without%20any%20interaction%20from%20the%20victim.%20This%20form%20of%20attack%20highlights%20the%20growing%20risks%20of%20spyware%20and%20how%20users%20can%20be%20unknowingly%20targeted%20without%20any%20action%20on%20their%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20WhatsApp%20official%20told%20%3Cem%3EReuters%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20the%20users%20were%20sent%20malicious%20electronic%20documents%20that%20required%20no%20user%20interaction%20to%20compromise%20their%20targets%2C%20a%20so-called%20zero-click%20hack%20that%20is%20considered%20particularly%20stealthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHackers%20targets%20were%20journalists%20and%20civil%20society%20members%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EReuters%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20WhatsApp%20officials%20declined%20to%20say%20who%2C%20specifically%2C%20was%20targeted.%20But%20he%20said%20those%20targeted%20were%20based%20in%20more%20than%20two%20dozen%20countries%2C%20including%20several%20people%20in%20Europe.%20However%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ftechnology%2F2025%2Fjan%2F31%2Fwhatsapp-israel-spyware%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20the%