cal%20toll%20of%20the%20treatment%20was%20exhausting%3B%20the%20young%20man%20endured%2012%20rounds%20of%20chemotherapy%2C%20each%20one%20taking%20an%20increasingly%20heavy%20toll%20on%20his%20body%2C%20and%20leaving%20him%20weaker%20and%20more%20vulnerable%20than%20the%20last.%20%E2%80%9CI%20lost%20my%20immunity%2C%20my%20hair%2C%20and%20all%20my%20energy.%20I%20would%20often%20feel%20nauseous%20and%20incredibly%20fatigued%20after%20each%20session%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20these%20difficult%20times%20that%20his%20brother%2C%20Srroth%20Bhartesh%2C%20emerged%20as%20his%20greatest%20pillar%20of%20support.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20days%20when%20Harteij%20hit%20rock%20bottom%2C%20and%20nothing%20seemed%20to%20help.%20But%20I%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20stay%20by%20his%20side%2C%20talk%20to%20him%2C%20and%20keep%20his%20mind%20occupied%20with%20positive%20thoughts%20to%20help%20him%20push%20through%2C%E2%80%9D%20Srroth%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20never%20spoke%20much%20about%20his%20condition%20to%20us.%20He%20wanted%20us%20to%20stay%20hopeful%2C%20even%20when%20things%20were%20tough.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20months%2C%20Harteij%E2%80%99s%20mother%20remained%20unaware%20of%20the%20severity%20of%20his%20illness.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20until%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F342777%2Fprevent-hair-loss-chemotherapy-cancer-care-raghuveer-surupa-eva-scalp-cooling-system-shark-tank%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseventh%20round%20of%20chemotherapy%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20family%20decided%20to%20reveal%20the%20truth.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20my%20mother%20arrived%20in%20Hyderabad%20to%20see%20me%2C%20everything%20felt%20better.%20Her%20food%20gave%20me%20the%20comfort%20and%20warmth%20that%20was%20missing%2C%E2%80%9D%20Harteij%20says%2C%20his%20voice%20tinged%20with%20emotion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-04-at-11.12.03-2-1738651569.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Harteij%20started%20his%20'Ride%20of%20Hope'%20initiative%20in%20May%202016%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-04-at-11.12.03-2-1738651569.jpeg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-04-at-11.12.03-2-1738651569-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-04-at-11.12.03-2-1738651569-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-04-at-11.12.03-2-1738651569-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-04-at-11.12.03-2-1738651569-800x600.jpeg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-04-at-11.12.03-2-1738651569-600x450.jpeg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-04-at-11.12.03-2-1738651569-400x300.jpeg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-04-at-11.12.03-2-1738651569-200x150.jpeg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-04-at-11.12.03-2-1738651569-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-403032%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHarteij%20started%20his%20%E2%80%98Ride%20of%20Hope%E2%80%99%20initiative%20in%20May%202016%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20undergoing%20treatment%2C%20he%20wanted%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20the%20disease.%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20where%20to%20start%20or%20what%20was%20the%20correct%20way%20to%20connect%20with%20fellow%20patients%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20treatment%2C%20Harteij%20moved%20to%20Raipur%20in%202015%20to%20rebuild%20his%20strength%20and%20immunity.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20doing%20yoga%2C%20going%20to%20the%20gym%2C%20anything%20I%20could%20do%20to%20get%20back%20to%20full%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20In%202016%2C%20he%20shifted%20to%20Pune%20to%20look%20for%20a%20job%2C%20but%20he%20quickly%20encountered%20challenges.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20CV%20had%20a%20three-year%20gap%2C%20which%20raised%20questions%20from%20employers.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20my%20eyebrows%20or%20hair%20back%20at%20that%20time%2C%20so%20people%20were%20naturally%20curious.%20When%20asked%2C%20I%20shared%20my%20cancer%20journey%20honestly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20his%20openness%2C%20some%20employers%20were%20sceptical%20about%20his%20ability%20to%20handle%20the%20pressures%20of%20a%20corporate%20job.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20employers%20who%20asked%20if%20I%20could%20cope%20with%20corporate%20life%20after%20everything%20I%20had%20been%20through%2C%20and%20some%20even%20turned%20me%20down%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20admits.%20This%20rejection%20led%20to%20a%20sense%20of%20frustration%20but%20also%20inspired%20him%20to%20take%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%2